%20of%20society%20that%20were%20once%20connections%20between%20people%20are%20turned%20into%20%26quot%3Bobjects%26quot%3B%20that%20become%20less%20interesting%20and%20meaningful%2C%20Lanier%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20you%20have%20the%20algorithms%20taking%20music%20from%20musicians%2C%20mashing%20it%20up%20into%20new%20music%2C%20and%20then%20not%20paying%20the%20musicians%2C%20gradually%20you%20start%20to%20undermine%20the%20economy%20because%20what%20happens%20to%20musicians%20now%20happens%20to%20everybody%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20Lanier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%2C%20while%20this%20year%20has%20been%20the%20%26quot%3Byear%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20next%20year%20the%20world%20is%20going%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bflooded%2C%20%3Cem%3Eflooded%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20AI-generated%20music.%26quot%3B%20With%20the%20release%20late%20last%20year%20of%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-senate-ai-forum-llama-2-gives-anthrax-instructions-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gptbot-ccbot-more-companies-block-ai-web-crawlers-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimitations%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20generative%20AI%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-killing-web-grand-bargain-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20deluge%20of%20generative%20AI%20content%2C%20from%20simple%20search%20prompts%20to%20eerie%20deepfakes%2C%20is%20now%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-copyright-office-new-rules-generative-ai-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20government%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuffington%2C%20who%20hosted%20the%20panel%20Lanier%20spoke%20on%2C%20called%20to%20Universal%20Music%20CEO%20Lucian%20Grainge%20in%20the%20cr