n't%20need%20to%20recreate%20the%20science%20fiction%20movies%20you%20grew%20up%20with.%26quot%3B%20Then%2C%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20an%20acceptance%20that%20without%20people%2C%20there%20is%20no%20data.%20Lanier%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fscience%2Fannals-of-artificial-intelligence%2Fthere-is-no-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewritten%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20and%20helped%20to%20define%20the%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3Bdata%20dignity%2C%26quot%3B%20wherein%20people%20are%20not%20effectively%20forced%20to%20hand%20over%20their%20personal%20data%20in%20exchange%20for%20using%20internet%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%2C%20however%2C%20people%20may%20have%20more%20power%20over%20their%20future%20success%20than%20they%20may%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20acknowledge%20that%20data%20comes%20from%20people%2C%20you%20have%20a%20future%20of%20an%20economy%20where%20people%20can%20be%20dignified%2C%20where%20people%20are%20acknowledged%2C%20where%20people%20can%20be%20inspired%2C%26quot%3B%20Lanier%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20the%20programs%20will%20get%20better%20because%20the%20people%20will%20be%20inspired%20to%20put%20better%20content%20into%20them.%20It%20just%20makes%20so%20much%20more%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20tech%20employee%20or%20someone%20else%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Kali%20Hays%20at%20khays%40insider.com%2C%20on%20secure%20messaging%20app%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignal.org%2Fdownload%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESignal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20at%20949-280-0267%2C%20or%20through%20Twitter%20DM%20at%20%40hayskali.%20Reach%20out%20using%20a%20non-work%20device.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-jaron-lanier-ai-advancing-without-human-dignity-undermines-everything