set%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6516e477b4518a00191e6af1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERick%20Stella%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUp%20to%2037%20days%20of%20battery%20life%2C%20deep%20offering%20of%20trackable%20activities%2C%20built-in%20flashlight%2C%20solar%20charging%20capability%2C%20available%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20sizes%2C%20insightful%20health%20tracking%20tools%2C%20accurate%20GPS%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EExpensive%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Epix%20Pro%20gets%20the%20nod%20as%20%26quot%3Bbest%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Fenix%207%20Pro%20is%20a%20very%20close%20second%2C%20thanks%20in%20large%20part%20to%20its%20multi-week%20battery%20life.%20This%20makes%20the%20Fenix%207%20Pro%20perfect%20for%20backpackers%2C%20marathon%20runners%2C%20or%20anyone%20who%20spends%20multiple%20hours%20and%20days%20active%20and%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20gives%20this%20watch%20such%20great%20battery%20capacity%20is%20its%20solar%20charging%20capability.%20By%20placing%20it%20in%20direct%20sunlight%20for%20up%20to%20three%20hours%2C%20the%20watch%20is%20able%20to%20squeeze%20out%20an%20extra%2022%20days%20while%20in%20smartwatch%20mode%20(with%20GPS%20turned%20off)%20and%20an%20extra%2073%20hours%20while%20in%20GPS%20mode.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20the%20Fenix%207%20Pro%20is%20capable%20of%20lasting%20over%20a%20month%20without%20a%20recharge%20is%20impressive.%20I%20never%20needed%20to%20put%20that%20time%20frame%20to%20the%20test%2C%20but%20I%20did%20take%20the%20watch%20on%20a%20few%20weekend%20camping%20trips%20and%20it%20was%20nice%20not%20having%20to%20worry%20about%20how%20I'd%20recharge%20it%20mid-weekend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20normal%20day-to-day%20use%2C%20where%20I%20preferred%20using%20the%20Always-On%20display%20and%20would%20use%20the%20GPS%20often%2C%20I'd%20get%20at%20least%20six%20days%20of%20battery%20life%2C%20if%20not%20a%20few%20more.%20This%20firmly%20puts%20the%20Fenix%207%20Pro%20at%20the%20head%20of%20the%20industry%20in%20terms%20of%20battery%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20the%20Fenix%207%20Pro%20is%20also%20an%20excellent%20health%20and%20fitness%20tracker.%20It's%20able%20to%20track%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20activities%20spanning%20everything%20from%20running%20and%20walking%20to%20hiking%2C%20cycling%2C%20swimming%2C%20and%20snowboarding.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20deep%20offering%20of%20health-tracking%20tools%20like%20an%20in-depth%20sleep%20tracker%2C%20a%20training%20readiness%20function%2C%20a%20stress%20monitor%2C%20and%20blood%20oxygen%20tracking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20diverse%20feature%20set%20gives%20the%20Fenix%207%20Pro%20similar%20utility%20to%20the%20Epix%20Pro.%20That%20is%2C%20it's%20best%20used%20by%20those%20who%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20majority%20of%20what's%20offered.%20And%20while%20there%20are%20%3Cem%3Ea%20lot%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20features%2C%20it%20never%20felt%20overwhelming%20from%20a%20user%20standpoint.%20I%20could%20customize%20what%20apps%20and%20tools%20were%20the%20most%20easily%20accessible%2C%20and%20anything%20I%20didn't%20use%20to%20just%20sit%20in%20the%20background%2C%20able%20to%20be%20accessed%20if%20or%20when%20I%20wanted%20(or%20never).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20this%20illustrates%20is%20that%20the%20Fenix%207%20Pro%20isn't%20just%20for%20one%20specific%20kind%20of%20user%20but%20rather%20it's%20multi-faceted%20enough%20to%20cater%20to%20active%20users%20and%20athletes%20of%20any%20skill%20level.%20Beginners%20can%20make%20use%20of%20the%20in-depth%20training%20data%20and%20recommended%20workouts%20to%20establish%20a%20new%20routine%20while%20advanced%20athletes%20can%20utilize%20the%20performance%20metrics%20and%20dynamic%20data%20to%20improve%20their%20overall%20fitness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20certain%20with%20the%20Fenix%207%20Pro%2C%20though%3A%20You'll%20hardly%20need%20to%20charge%20it%2C%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20fall%20on%20the%20user%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20smartwatch%3A%20Garmin%20Venu%203%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20holding%20a%20Garmin%20Venu%203%20smartwatch%20in%20their%20hand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6516e4dbf5d0bb0019e5afeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAllows%20you%20to%20make%20and%20receive%20calls%20right%20on%20the%20watch%2C%20unique%20and%20intuitive%20new%20interface%2C%20in-depth%20sleep%20tracking%20and%20coaching%2C%20advanced%20fitness%20tracking%20tools%20but%20in%20a%20user-friendly%20smartwatch%20package%2C%20available%20in%20two%20sizes%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%20LTE%20option%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20many%20of%20Garmin's%20best%20wearables%20are%20advanced%20GPS%20watches%20packing%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20health%20and%20fitness%20tracking%20tools%2C%20it%20also%20makes%20a%20quality%20smartwatch%20called%20the%20Venu.%20The%20Venu%203%20is%20the%20next%20iteration%20of%20the%20line%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgarmin-venu-2-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewe%20loved%20the%20Venu%202%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20it%20strikes%20an%20excellent%20balance%20between%20being%20smart%20and%20sporty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20receiving%20notifications%20for%20things%20like%20texts%2C%20emails%2C%20calls%2C%20and%20apps%2C%20the%20Venu%203's%20biggest%20new%20smartwatch%20feature%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20make%20and%20receive%20phone%20calls.%20The%20watch%20needs%20to%20be%20tethered%20to%20a%20smartphone%20for%20this%20to%20work%20(there's%20no%20LTE%20version%20available)%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20convenient%20feature.%20This%20isn't%20something%20I%20used%20all%20the%20time%20but%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20have%20access%20to%20if%20my%20phone%20was%20in%20another%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Venu%203's%20interface%20is%20also%20quite%20a%20bit%20different%20than%20what%20I'm%20used%20to%20with%20other%20Garmin%20wearables%20like%20the%20Epix%2C%20Fenix%2C%20or%20Forerunner%20series.%20The%20experience%20felt%20far%20more%20smartwatch-centric%20and%20less%20like%20a%20fitness%20tracker%20that%20gets%20phone%20notifications.%20This%20is%20due%20in%20large%20part%20to%20its%20bright%2C%20colorful%20AMOLED%20touchscreen%20display.%20Coupled%20with%20a%20fluid%20and%20intuitive%20interface%2C%20it%20sort%20of%20has%20a%20similar%20feel%20to%20using%20something%20like%20Android's%20Wear%20OS%20or%20iPhone's%20Watch%20OS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20that%20interface%2C%20it%20feels%20entirely%20different%20to%20use%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20than%20the%20Epix%20Pro%20or%20Fenix%207%20Pro.%20Those%20watches%20are%20geared%20toward%20active%20users%20and%20have%20basic%20smartwatch%20functionality%2C%20whereas%20the%20Venu%203%20is%20a%20bonafide%20smartwatch%2C%20and%20did%20a%20good%20job%20of%20acting%20as%20an%20effective%20extension%20of%20my%20smartphone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20still%20offer%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20health%20and%20fitness%20tracking%20tools%2C%20like%20compatibility%20with%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20activities%2C%20an%20in-depth%20sleep%20tracker%20and%20coach%2C%20a%20stress%20monitor%2C%20and%20adaptive%20training.%20These%20all%20function%20similarly%20to%20the%20Epix%20or%20Fenix%2C%20so%20rest%20assured%20the%20Venu%203%20isn't%20a%20watered-down%20activity%20tracker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20running%20watch%3A%20Garmin%20Forerunner%20745%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Garmin%20Forerunner%20745%20smartwatch%20on%20a%20person's%20wrist.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6516e261b4518a00191e6a0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Molina%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUnique%20adaptive%20training%20recommendations%2C%20offers%20access%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20fitness%20data%2C%20allows%20for%20deep%20customization%2C%20accurate%20and%20quick%20GPS%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESlightly%20cumbersome%20menu%20system%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20wearable%20that%20takes%20the%20guesswork%20out%20of%20creating%20and%20sticking%20to%20a%20running%20plan%2C%20the%20Forerunner%20745%20is%20what%20you%20seek%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-running-watch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20running%20watch%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Garmin's%20lineup.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20every%20single%20bell%20and%20whistle%20like%20the%20Epix%20Pro%20but%20that's%20a%20good%20thing%3B%20it%20offers%20just%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20workout%20options%2C%20training%20feedback%2C%20and%20recovery%20insight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20training%20feedback%20and%20recommendation%20feature%20is%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20745%2C%20and%20it%20offers%20more%20than%20just%20basic%20workout%20suggestions%20and%20insight.%20Instead%2C%20it%20adapts%20to%20a%20user's%20weekly%20training%20schedule%20while%20also%20factoring%20in%20their%20recovery%20rate.%20Based%20on%20how%20well%20they've%20rested%20each%20day%2C%20it%20recommends%20certain%20distances%2C%20pacing%2C%20and%20exertion.%20For%20instance%2C%20one%20day%20it%20may%20recommend%20a%2030-minute%20run%20at%20a%2010-minute%20pace%20but%20then%20recommend%20a%20sprint%20workout%20for%20later%20in%20the%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20a%20user's%20performance%20during%20each%20workout%2C%20the%20745%20can%20assess%20the%20training%20data%20to%20see%20how%20much%20of%20an%20impact%20is%20being%20made%20on%20their%20endurance%20and%20speed.%20It%20also%20provides%20training%20load%20feedback%2C%20recovery%20time%20recommendations%2C%20and%20status%20updates%20all%20based%20on%20that%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20this%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20data%20to%20digest%20at%20once%2C%20it's%20presented%20in%20an%20easy-to-read%20manner%20that's%20intuitive%20to%20navigate.%20Much%20of%20it%20is%20displayed%20post-workout%2C%20too%2C%20so%20you%20can%20always%20get%20an%20up-to-date%20look%20at%20your%20weekly%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20745%20is%20also%20an%20adequate%20health%20tracker%2C%20offering%20tools%20like%20in-depth%20sleep%20tracking%20and%20insight%2C%20menstrual%20cycle%20tracking%2C%20and%20blood%20oxygen%20monitoring.%20It%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20smartwatch%20features%2C%20as%20well%2C%20such%20as%20basic%20notifications%20for%20calls%2C%20texts%2C%20and%20apps%2C%20along%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20download%20and%20play%20music%20and%20contactless%20payment%20via%20Garmin%20Pay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgarmin-forerunner-745-review%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20our%20full%20review%20of%20the%20Garmin%20Forerunner%20745%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20multi-sport%20watch%3A%20Garmin%20Forerunner%20945%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221598%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20using%20the%20training%20status%20function%20on%20a%20Garmin%20Forerunner%20945%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65170ea311c4f90019914ceb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGarmin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDeep%20offering%20of%20