%20and%20cycling%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20deep%20offering%20of%20health%20tools%20like%20sleep%20tracking%2C%20energy%20monitoring%2C%20rest%20and%20recovery%20recommendations%2C%20women's%20health%20tracking%2C%20and%20a%20blood%20oxygen%20monitor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20provides%20basic%20smartwatch%20functionality%20as%20well%2C%20offering%20notifications%20for%20things%20like%20calls%20and%20texts%2C%20while%20also%20supporting%20contactless%20payment%20via%20Garmin%20Pay.%20There%20are%20also%20a%20few%20safety%20features%20such%20as%20incident%20detection%20that%20can%20automatically%20call%20an%20emergency%20contact%20in%20the%20event%20of%20some%20form%20of%20accident%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20feature%20called%20LiveTrack%20which%20transmits%20your%20location%20in%20real-time%20to%20anyone%20you%20add%20as%20a%20friend%20or%20family%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watch%20does%20have%20one%20drawback%20that%20may%20limit%20its%20overall%20appeal%3A%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20best%20battery%20life.%20With%20GPS%20mode%20enabled%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20to%20get%20around%2010%20to%2012%20hours%20of%20battery%2C%20which%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20other%20watches%20in%20this%20guide.%20This%20should%20still%20be%20good%20enough%20for%20a%20marathon%20or%20short-distance%20triathlon%2C%20but%20anyone%20who%20competes%20in%20longer%20races%20should%20look%20at%20other%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20Garmin%20watch%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20a%20Garmin%20watch%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20how%20you%20plan%20on%20using%20it.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20need%20offline%20map%20support%2C%20a%20built-in%20flashlight%2C%20or%20tracking%20capability%20for%20every%20sport%20imaginable%2C%20then%20you%20likely%20don't%20need%20to%20spend%20%24900%20on%20something%20like%20the%20Epix%20Pro.%20Instead%2C%20you%20can%20opt%20for%20a%20watch%20like%20the%20Forerunner%20745%20or%20even%20the%20Venu%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20how%20you%20intend%20to%20use%20the%20watch%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20determine%20which%20model%20fits%20your%20lifestyle.%20Here's%20what%20else%20to%20consider%20before%20purchasing%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20case%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUse%20case%20is%20vital%20as%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20main%20factors%20that%20determines%20which%20model%20is%20best%20for%20you.%20Many%20Garmin%20watches%20offer%20similar%20sets%20of%20features%20but%20some%20are%20better%20suited%20for%20certain%20users.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Forerunner%20series%20is%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20runners%20and%20multi-sport%20athletes%20as%20it%20has%20plenty%20of%20running-specific%20features%20and%20training%20tools.%20Similarly%2C%20avid%20outdoors%20people%20may%20want%20to%20look%20at%20the%20Epix%20Pro%20or%20Fenix%207%20Pro%2C%20two%20wearables%20that%20offer%20accurate%20GPS%2C%20offline%20map%20support%2C%20a%20rugged%20design%2C%20and%20multi-week%20battery%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMany%20Garmin%20watches%20are%20available%20in%20a%20few%20different%20sizes%20with%20some%20lines%2C%20like%20the%20Venu%2C%20available%20in%20a%20small-specific%20model.%20These%20smaller%20models%20carry%20an%20%26quot%3BS%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20product%20name%2C%20so%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Venu%203%2C%20the%20smaller%20version%20is%20titled%20the%20Venu%203S.%20Other%20watches%2C%20like%20the%20Epix%20Pro%2C%20are%20available%20in%20multiple%20sizing%20options.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20life%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20battery%20life%20native%20to%20Garmin%20watches%20varies%2C%20as%20some%20offer%20up%20to%20as%20many%20as%20several%20weeks%20of%20life%20(like%20the%20Epix%20Pro%20and%20Fenix%207%20Pro)%20while%20others%20need%20to%20be%20recharged%20daily%20(like%20the%20Forerunner%20945).%20If%20you%20travel%20often%20or%20aren't%20always%20near%20a%20