lable%20in%20a%20sizing%20option%20that%20wasn't%20too%20big%20or%20too%20small%20for%20our%20wrists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAny%20advanced%20fitness%20tracker%2C%20like%20most%20Garmins%2C%20is%20going%20to%20require%20some%20bit%20of%20a%20learning%20curve%2C%20especially%20for%20first-time%20users.%20Garmin's%20interface%20isn't%20exactly%20beginner-friendly%20but%20the%20learning%20curve%20isn't%20super%20steep.%20Some%20interfaces%20offer%20a%20more%20intuitive%20experience%2C%20like%20the%20Venu%203%2C%20but%20every%20Garmin%20watch%20in%20this%20guide%20can%20easily%20be%20mastered%20after%20spending%20just%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValue%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EValue%20is%20tough%20to%20nail%20down%20with%20fitness%20trackers%2C%20especially%20when%20comparing%20watches%20that%20vary%20so%20wildly%20in%20price%20like%20Garmin's%20do.%20On%20one%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20is%20the%20%24900%20Epix%20Pro%2C%20a%20watch%20that%20carries%20a%20ton%20of%20value%20to%20hardcore%20athletes%20and%20those%20who%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20outside.%20Is%20%24900%20expensive%3F%20Absolutely%2C%20but%20if%20you%20use%20most%20of%20the%20features%20available%2C%20then%20it's%20worth%20the%20investment.%20You%20may%20have%20to%20spend%20%24900%20but%20that%20watch%20will%20serve%20you%20for%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3EDoes%20a%20Garmin%20watch%20work%20with%20any%20smartphone%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Garmin%20watches%20are%20compatible%20with%20smartphones%20running%20either%20iOS%20or%20Android.%20Plus%2C%20the%20experience%20is%20almost%20identical%20since%20both%20phone%20formats%20use%20the%20Garmin%20Connect%20app%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20watch.%20If%20there%20are%20any%20small%20differences%2C%20it's%20due%20mainly%20to%20how%20an%20iOS%20or%20Android%20device%20functions%2C%20not%20because%20of%20an%20incompatibility%20w