20in%20a%20case%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-debt-relief-borrowers-cfpb-scotus-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecould%20have%20major%20implications%20for%20consumers%20nationwide%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20hear%20oral%20arguments%20in%20the%20case%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scotusblog.com%2Fcase-files%2Fcases%2Fconsumer-financial-protection-bureau-v-community-financial-services-association-of-america-limited%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20v.%C2%A0Community%20Financial%20Services%20Association%20of%20America%20Ltd.%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20argues%20the%20CFPB's%20independent%20funding%20structure%20is%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20establishment%20in%202011%2C%20the%20CFPB%20has%20relied%20on%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20for%20funding%20rather%20than%20Congress'%20annual%20appropriations%20process%2C%20which%20the%20Fifth%20Circuit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felizabeth-warren-blasts-fifth-circuit-cfpb-funding-unconstitutional-student-loans-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruled%20last%20year%20is%20illegal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20now%20taking%20on%20the%20case%2C%20and%20Sheila%20Bair%20%E2%80%94%20the%20former%20chair%20of%20the%20Federal%20Deposit%20Insurance%20Corporation%20%E2%80%94%20raised%20the%20risks%20of%20an%20adverse%20ruling%20in%20a%20Politico%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2Fmagazine%2F2023%2F09%2F28%2Fsupreme-court-social-security-medicare-00118470%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopinion%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opinion%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20sea%20change%20in%20how%20essential%20government%20agencies%20function%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20potential%20chaos%20every%20time%20Congress%20engages%20in%20brinkmanship%20over%20funding%2C%26quot%3B%20Bair%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEssential%20government%20agencies%20and%20programs%2C%20including%20Social%20Security%20and%20Medicare%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20administered%20by%20independently%20funded%20bodies%2C%20would%20see%20their%20sources%20of%20independent%20funding%20vulnerable%20to%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%20responsible%20for%20monetary%20policy%20and%20our%20payments%20system%2C%20would%20be%20particularly%20at%20risk%2C%20given%20that%20it%20runs%20on%20fees%20and%20profits%20from%20its%20market%20operations%20just%20like%20the%20CFPB.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20Bair%20said%2C%20deciding%20the%20CFPB%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20independently%20funded%20would%20open%20the%20floodgates%20for%20legal%20challenges%20against%20every%20other%20agency%20with%20a%20similar%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efunding%20structure.%20It%20would%20also%20jeopardize%20those%20agencies'%20operations%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20government%20shutdown%2C%20for%20example%2C%20if%20their%20funding%20relied%20on%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBair%20referenced%20the%202008%20financial%20crisis%2C%20during%20which%20she%20was%20serving%20as%20chair%20of%20the%20FDIC.%20She%20said%20the%20agency's%20independent%20structure%20allowed%20it%20to%20quickly%20boost%20funding%20to%20protect%20Main%20Street%20bank%20depositors%2C%20and%20without%20that%20structure%2C%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20could%20have%20suffered%20delayed%20access%20to%20their%20insured%20deposit%20accounts%20as%20their%20failed%20banks%20shuttered%20until%20Congress%20saw%20fit%20to%20fund%20the%20agency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20those%20concerns%2C%20the%20lenders%20that%20brought%20the%20lawsuit%20wrote%20in%20their%20legal%20filing%20that%20the%20CFPB%20should%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bas%20much%20as%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20directly%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20each%20year%20forever.%26quot%3B%20Congress%20ensured%20in%20the%202010%20Dodd-Frank%20Wall%20Street%20Reform%20and%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%20that%20the%20CFPB%20could%20request%20funding%20from%20the%20Fed%20so%20long%20as%20its%20request%20never%20exceeds%20%24597%20million%2C%20adjusted%20for%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20advocates%20and%20lawmakers%20have%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20the%20CFPB's%20funding%20structure%20to%20protect%20consumers%20from%20the%20potential%20fallout.%20Shahid%20Naeem%2C%20a%20senior%20policy%20analyst%20at%20the%20nonprofit%20American%20Economic%20Liberties%20Project%2C%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-debt-relief-borrowers-cfpb-scotus-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20look%20at%20the%20parties%20involved%20in%20this%20case%2C%20you%20have%20a%20payday-lending%20lobby%20and%20then%20you%20have%20the%20CFPB%2C%20which%20was%20birthed%20out%20of%20the%202008%20financial%20crisis%20by%20Congress%20as%20a%20way%20of%20protecting%20Americans%20from%20the%20kind%20of%20predatory%20and%20exploitative%20financial-services%20practices%20that%20got%20us%20into%202008%20and%20various%20other%20crises%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CFPB%20has%20performed%20a%20range%20of%20oversight%20actions%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20including%20cracking%20down%20on%20predatory%20behaviors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-debt-relief-borrowers-cfpb-scotus-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20have%20cost%20student-loan%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Massachusetts%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%2C%20who%20spearheaded%20the%20CFPB's%20creation%2C%20said%20during%20a%20speech%20last%20week%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20CFPB%20is%20the%20cop%20on%20the%20beat%20for%20the%20finances%20of%20America's%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CFPB%20is%20future%20is%20at%20stake%20in%20this%20court%20decision%2C%20along%20with%20the%20future%20of%20every%20other%20banking%20regulator%2C%26quot%3B%20Warren%20continued.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20possible%20fallout%20doesn't%20stop%20there.%20Social%20Security%20and%20Medicare%20are%20also%20operated%20outside%20the%20annual%20appropriations%20process.%20A%20bad%20decision%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20could%20wreck%20the%20financial%20security%20of%20millions%20of%20families%20and%20turn%20our%20economy%20upside%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-medicare-federal-programs-vulnerable-cfpb-supreme-court-fdic-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696277094000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651b18b72ce014759e72a61d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-medicare-federal-programs-vulnerable-cfpb-supreme-court-fdic-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20hear%20a%20case%20challenging%20the%20funding%20structure%20of%20the%20CFPB.%20A%20former%20FDIC%20official%20said%20it%20could%20harm%20consumers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-medicare-federal-programs-vulnerable-cfpb-supreme-court-fdic-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Daniel%20Radcliffe%20Remembers%20Dumbledore%20Actor%20Michael%20Gambon%3A%20%E2%80%98His%20True%20Passion%20Was%20Restoring%2019th-Century%20Dueling%20Pistols%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696277090000