A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwest-comes-to-east-to-learn-the-art-of-shaadi-planning%2Farticleshow%2F104113829.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ASHISH%20MEHTA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwest-comes-to-east-to-learn-the-art-of-shaadi-planning%2Farticleshow%2F104113829.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airlines%20want%20you%20to%20lose%20weight.%20Ozempic%20could%20save%20them%20millions.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20boxes%20of%20Wegovy%20on%20a%20light%20wood%20counter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651aedcc4ff1e30019477159%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWeight%20loss%20drugs%20like%20Wegovy%20and%20Ozempic%20have%20become%20so%20popular%20over%20the%20last%20year%20that%20there%20have%20been%20shortages.%3Cp%3Epicture%20alliance%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EAirlines%20are%20consistently%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20reduce%20plane%20weight%20to%20increase%20fuel%20efficiency.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20rise%20in%20popularity%20of%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-ozempic-wegovy-actually-work-telling-brain-to-feel-full-2023-3%5C%22%3EOzempic%20and%20Wegovy%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20benefit%20airlines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOne%20analyst%20estimated%20United%20would%20save%20%2480%20million%20a%20year%20if%20every%20passenger%20lost%2010%20pounds.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20boom%20of%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20and%20other%20buzzy%20weight-loss%20drugs%20could%20do%20more%20than%20just%20help%20people%20lose%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20it%20could%20help%20the%20airline%20industry%20save%20money%20on%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20consistent%20cost-saving%20focus%20of%20airlines%20has%20been%20to%20minimize%20the%20weight%20of%20each%20plane.%20The%20heavier%20an%20aircraft%20is%2C%20the%20harder%20the%20engines%20have%20to%20work%2C%20resulting%20in%20more%20fuel%20being%20needed%20for%20the%20plane%20to%20operate.%20Airlines%20have%20made%20food%20and%20drink%20carts%20lighter%2C%20installed%20lighter%20entertainment%20systems%2C%20switched%20to%20more%20lightweight%20seats%2C%20and%20even%20printed%20pamphlets%20and%20magazines%20on%20lighter%20paper%2C%20all%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-airlines-are-cutting-weight-2013-4%23now-see-the-future-of-flying-in-luxury-12%5C%22%3Ecut%20down%20on%20the%20overall%20weight%20of%20their%20planes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20mandates%20that%20airlines%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fformer-emirates-staff-say-cabin-crew-monitored-weight-police-2022-1%5C%22%3Eweight%20of%20crew%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20account%20when%20calculating%20how%20heavy%20a%20plane%20is%20overall%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-airline-weigh-passengers-scales-boarding-gates-before-flights-2023-8%5C%22%3EKorean%20airlines%20weighed%20its%20passengers%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20boarding%20for%20a%20period%20this%20year%20to%20collect%20data%20on%20passenger%20weights%20and%20comply%20with%20local%20laws.%20It's%20unlikely%2C%20though%2C%20that%20most%20airlines%20would%20ever%20enforce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-check-ins-weight-watchers-scenario-customers-says-experts-2021-6%5C%22%3Emandatory%20weighing%20of%20passengers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20comply%20with%20safety%20limits%2C%20two%20industry%20experts%20previously%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20unclear%20how%20wide%20an%20impact%20the%20spread%20of%20weight-loss%20drugs%20will%20actually%20have%20on%20average%20passenger%20weights%2C%20Sheila%20Kahyaoglu%2C%20a%20Jefferies%20Financial%20analyst%2C%20estimated%20in%20a%20recent%20report%20on%20the%20implications%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bslimmer%20society%26quot%3B%20that%20airlines%20could%20save%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20money%20if%20the%20average%20passenger%20lost%20weight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20United%20Airlines%20as%20a%20model%2C%20Kahyaoglu%20estimated%20that%20if%20each%20passenger%20weighed%2010%20pounds%20less%20on%20average%2C%20the%20weight%20savings%20would%20equal%20around%201%2C790%20pounds%20per%20flight.%20Referencing%20a%20past%20example%20of%20the%20airline%20cutting%20down%20aircraft%20weight%2C%20she%20estimates%20that%20the%20airline%20would%20save%2027.6%20million%20gallons%20of%20fuel%20per%20year%2C%20or%20around%20%2480%20million%20worth%20going%20by%20the%20average%20price%20of%20fuel%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20reported%20in%202021%20that%20the%20average%20weight%20of%20passengers%20had%20increased%20%E2%80%94%20American%20Airlines%20told%20Insider%20at%20the%20time%20that%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbmi-is-bogus-best-way-to-tell-if-youre-a-healthy-weight-2016-9%5C%22%3Eaverage%20passenger%20was%20eight%20pounds%20heavier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20182%20pounds%20in%20summer%20and%20187%20pounds%20in%20winter.%20Both%20American%20and%20Southwest%20Airlines%20previously%20told%20Insider%20that%20they%20use%20data%20from%20the%20CDC%20to%20calculate%20passenger%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20CDC%20data%20covers%202015-2018%20(the%20same%20data%20available%20in%202021)%20and%20shows%20the%20average%20US%20male%20over%20the%20age%20of%2020%20weighs%20199.8%20pounds%2C%20while%20the%20average%20US%20woman%20weighs%20170.8%20pounds.%20Both%20averages%20had%20increased%20from%20the%20previous%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20class%20of%20game-changer%20weight-loss%20drugs%2C%20repurposed%20from%20diabetes%20treatment%20%E2%80%94%20semaglutide%2C%20which%20marketed%20as%20Ozempic%20for%20diabetes%20and%20Wegovy%20for%20weight%20loss%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-weight-loss-meds-injections-compare-costs-results-side-effects%5C%22%3Etirzepatide%2C%20and%20liraglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20has%20gained%20mainstream%20attention%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20especially%20as%20some%20of%20the%20rich%20and%20famous%20have%20taken%20the%20drug%20(or%20denied%20that%20they've%20taken%20it).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Felon-musk-weight-loss-drug-wegovy-semaglutide-fit-ripped-healthy-2022-10%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20he%20lost%2020%20pounds%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-hes-tried-intermittent-fasting-now-feels-healthier-2022-8%5C%22%3EWegovy%20and%20intermittent%20fasting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Boris%20Johnson%2C%20Amy%20Schumer%2C%20Charles%20Barkley%2C%20and%20Sharon%20Osbourne%2C%20have%20all%20said%20they%20have%20taken%20semaglutide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fozempic-hollywood-weightloss-drug-popular-with-nyc-rich-2023-4%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%20plastic%20surgeon%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20Insider%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20I%20say%20everybody%20is%20on%20it%2C%20it's%20like%2C%20%3Cem%3Eeverybody%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20on%20it.%26quot%3B%20The%20high%20demand%20for%20the%20drug%20has%20led%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fnew-weight-loss-drugs-popularity-evidence-and-side-effects-2022-11%5C%22%3Ewidespread%20shortages%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recent%20CDC%20data%20covering%20the%20time%20since%20these%20new%20weight-loss%20drugs%20gained%20popularity%20hasn't%20become%20available%20yet%20%E2%80%94%20time%20will%20tell%20how%20widespread%20the%20effect%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-wegovy-weight-loss-drugs-airlines-fue