%20chair%20starts%20from%20just%20%24110%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20the%20cheapest%20option%20on%20our%20list%20by%20a%20distance.%20You%20can%20get%20it%20in%20various%20colors%2C%20including%20red%20and%20black%2C%20blue%20and%20black%2C%20or%20plain%20black%20in%20the%20polyurethane%20covering.%20While%20the%20polyurethane%20wipes%20clean%20easily%2C%20it%20can%20also%20get%20sweaty%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20something%20you%20want%20against%20your%20skin%2C%20so%20you%20may%20prefer%20to%20pay%20a%20little%20more%20for%20a%20fabric%20finish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20chair%20feels%20reasonably%20sturdy%20and%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20emulating%20more%20expensive%20gaming%20chairs%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20the%20difference%20when%20you%20sit%20in%20it.%20This%20is%20a%20budget%20gaming%20chair%2C%20and%20the%20quality%20reflects%20that.%20We%20can't%20speak%20to%20longevity%20either.%20Online%20research%20reveals%20reports%20about%20different%20faults%20and%20parts%20of%20this%20chair%20breaking.%20Customer%20service%20looks%20to%20be%20good%2C%20but%20we%20have%20some%20concerns%20about%20long-term%20durability.%20Ultimately%2C%20although%20there%20are%20better%20gaming%20chairs%2C%20we%20can't%20find%20a%20superior%20option%20at%20this%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20office%20model%3A%20Steelcase%20Leap%20V2%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221189%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steelcase%20Leap%20V2%20chair%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20a%20room%20behind%20a%20desk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651aed204ff1e30019477109%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22892%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESimon%20Hill%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpholstery%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Polyester%20or%20leather%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMax%20height%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20specified%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20limit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20400%20pounds%3C%