20require%20extra%20accessories%2C%20like%20an%20HDMI%20Audio%20Extractor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20X-Rocker%20Pro%20Series%202.1%20delivers%20surprisingly%20decent%20sound%2C%20and%20the%20vibrations%20add%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20experience%20to%20gaming%20sessions%20and%20movies.%20A%20panel%20on%20the%20right-hand%20side%20houses%20controls%20and%20various%20wired%20connections.%20Assembly%20is%20required%2C%20and%20you'll%20want%20help%20to%20do%20so.%20Once%20it's%20put%20together%2C%20the%20chair%20feels%20pretty%20sturdy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high-quality%20speakers%20and%20vibrations%20make%20this%20chair%20fantastic%20for%20fast-paced%20games.%20Racing%20game%20enthusiasts%20in%20particular%20will%20get%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20the%20chair's%20immersive%20sound%20and%20feel.%20It's%20also%20foldable%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20store%20when%20you're%20not%20using%20it%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20more%20rigid%20gaming%20chairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20X-Rocker%20Pro%20Series%202.1%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20offer%20for%20around%20%24250%2C%20but%20if%20you%20don't%20care%20about%20the%20sound%20or%20vibration%20features%2C%20you%20should%20check%20out%20a%20more%20comfortable%2C%20adjustable%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20a%20wide%20seat%3A%20AndaSeat%20Kaiser%203%20XL%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20AndaSeat%20Kaiser%203%20XL%20gaming%20chair%20next%20to%20a%20black%20version.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651aee5cecc9f4001942a46b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22562%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAndaSeat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpholstery%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20PVC%20leather%20or%20linen%20fabric%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMax%20height%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%206'11%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20limit%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20395%20pounds%3C%2Fli%3E