tably%20the%20Vantum%2C%20made%20in%20cooperation%20with%20gaming%20accessory%20titan%20Logitech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vantum%20is%20a%20stylish%20gaming%20chair%20that's%20designed%20to%20be%20used%20for%20long%20stretches%20of%20time%20without%20breaks.%20It's%20made%20with%20a%20soft%20polyurethane%20fabric%2C%20and%20has%20a%20suspension%20structure%20that%20encourages%20breathable%20airflow.%20Its%20neckpad%20helps%20support%20both%20your%20neck%20and%20spine%20to%20combat%20aches%20and%20pains.%20And%20its%20solid%20glass-filled%20frame%20means%20that%20it%20can%20support%20up%20to%20350%20pounds%2C%20which%20is%20great%20for%20a%20chair%20this%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20other%20chairs%2C%20the%20Vantum%20is%20also%20incredibly%20customizable.%20Using%20the%20built-in%20knobs%2C%20you%20can%20adjust%20the%20seat%20depth%2C%20chair%20height%2C%20neckpad%20position%2C%20back%20curve%2C%20maximum%20tilt%20angle%2C%20and%20even%20tilt%20tension.%20All%20these%20knobs%20are%20also%20etched%20with%20numeric%20markings%20that%20let%20you%20keep%20track%20of%20exactly%20which%20settings%20you%20like.%20If%20you're%20fussy%20about%20your%20gaming%20chair's%20exact%20positioning%20and%20feel%2C%20the%20Vantum%20might%20be%20your%20true%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vantum's%20only%20major%20downside%20is%20that%20it%20can't%20recline%20very%20far.%20According%20to%20the%20Herman%20Miller%20website's%20Q%26amp%3BA%20section%2C%20the%20Vantum%20can%20only%20recline%20about%2019%C2%B0%20from%20its%20default%20upright%20position.%20That's%20a%20far%20shallower%20tilt%20than%20other%20chairs.%20You%20also%20can't%20lock%20the%20chair%20in%20a%20reclined%20position%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20to%20actively%20push%20back%20on%20the%20seat.%20And%20the%20chair's%20default%20position%20actually%20pushes%20you%20forward%20slightly%2C%20which%20won't%20be%20to%20everyone's%20liking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Vantum's%20biggest%20strengths%20is%20its%20price.%20Herman