0suited%20to%20your%20height%20and%20weight.%20You'll%20generally%20find%20a%20suggested%20range%20or%20maximum%20height%20and%20weight%20in%20the%20specs%20of%20each%20chair.%20Bear%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20ideal%20height%20and%20weight%20for%20a%20chair%20will%20likely%20be%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20stated%20range.%20This%20is%20especially%20important%20if%20the%20chair%20isn't%20adjustable%20or%20has%20limited%20adjustability.%20Make%20sure%20you%20read%20reviews%20and%20see%20what%20people%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20sizing.%20If%20you%20can%2C%20it's%20always%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20try%20before%20you%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjustability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20best%20gaming%20chairs%20will%20be%20fully%20adjustable%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20tailor%20the%20chair%20to%20your%20body.%20Ideally%2C%20you%20should%20be%20able%20to%20adjust%20the%20seat%20height%20and%20the%20armrests%20and%20tilt%20and%20recline%20in%20the%20chair.%20The%20best%20gaming%20chairs%20will%20also%20offer%20adjustable%20lumbar%20support%20and%20extras%20like%20seat%20depth%20adjustments%2C%20but%20these%20are%20often%20lacking%20in%20cheaper%20chairs.%20Bear%20in%20mind%20that%20you%20can%20always%20add%20a%20cushion%20for%20lumbar%20support%2C%20but%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20get%20one%20that%20can%20be%20strapped%20into%20the%20correct%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20majority%20of%20our%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20gaming%20chairs%20are%20finished%20in%20polyurethane%20(PU)%20leather%2C%20but%20you%20can%20also%20find%20fabric%20finishes%20and%20real%20leather%20chairs%2C%20though%20they%20will%20be%20more%20expensive.%20Fake%20or%20real%20leather%20has%20the%20advantage%20of%20being%20easy%20to%20wipe%20clean%20but%20can%20lead%20to%20an%20uncomfortably%20sweaty%20back.%20Fabric%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20breathable%20but%20may%20stain%20more%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStyle%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20can%20get%20gaming%20chairs%20emblazoned%20with%20esports%20logos%20or%20styled%20after%20videogame%20characters%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20buying%20something%20for%20the%20home%20office%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20consider%20what%20the%20chair%20will%20look%20like%20during%20a%20business%20video%20call.%20Some%20options%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20traditional%20office%20chair%20and%20gaming%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20gaming%20chairs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Secretlab%20Titan%203%20gaming%20chair%20in%20the%20corner%20of%20a%20room%20behind%20a%20desk%20with%20two%20monitors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651af05becc9f4001942a52e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESimon%20Hill%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20built%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20gaming%20chairs%20using%20a%20mix%20of%20first-hand%20testing%20and%20thorough%20research.%20When%20evaluating%20which%20gaming%20chairs%20are%20worth%20highlighting%2C%20we%20prioritize%20a%20variety%20of%20criteria%2C%20including%20comfort%2C%20skeletal%20support%2C%20price%2C%20design%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20even%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20chair's%20warranty.%20Occasionally%2C%20we%20may%20recommend%20a%20chair%20that%20falters%20in%20some%20categories%20if%20it%20significantly%20excels%20in%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20guide%2C%20we%20also%20gathered%20recommendations%20from%20game%20developers%20and%20avid%20gamers.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20cross-referenced%20our%20opinions%20with%20existing%20gaming%20chair%20reviews%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20weren't%20missing%20any%20hidden%20gems%2C%20or%20making%20anecdotal%20claims%20that%20don't%20hold%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20Insider%20reviewers%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20industries%20they%20write%20about%2C%20and%20we%20re-evaluate%20our%20buying%20guides%20multiple%20times%20per%20year.%20This%20helps%20us%20write%20the%20most%20accurate%20reviews%20and%20recommendations%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGaming%20chair%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20best%20gaming%20chairs%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ebc39c0cdfd480e4e764032%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGT%20Racing%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20much%20money%20will%20a%20good%20gaming%20chair%20cost%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGaming%20chairs%20can%20get%20pretty%20expensive.%20A%20budget%20gaming%20chair%20comes%20in%20around%20%24150%20to%20%24300%2C%20but%20these%20chairs%20are%20usually%20missing%20features%20and%20aren't%20super%20comfortable.%20You%20can%20find%20chairs%20for%20lower%20than%20this%2C%20but%20they're%20rarely%20even%20worth%20considering.%20Normal%20gaming%20chairs%20%E2%80%94%20like%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20SecretLab%20Titan%20Evo%202022%20%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20range%20from%20%24500%20to%20%24800.%20These%20are%20the%20comfortable%20chairs%20that%20feature%20adjustable%20parts%2C%20lumbar%20support%2C%20and%20sturdy%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20pass%20the%20%24800%20mark%2C%20you'll%20start%20seeing%20diminishing%20returns.%20Premium%20furniture%20brands%20like%20Herman%20Miller%20make%20fantastic%20chairs%20that%20feel%20wonderful%20to%20sit%20in%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time%2C%20but%20they're%20probably%20not%20so%20much%20better%20that%20they're%20worth%20breaking%20the%20bank%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDoes%20every%20gaming%20chair%20fit%20every%20body%20type%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo.%20Some%20gaming%20chairs%20will%20be%20too%20thin%20to%20sit%20comfortably%20in%2C%20some%20will%20be%20too%20short%20to%20avoid%20cramping%20long%20legs%2C%20and%20so%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20gaming%20chairs%20are%20adjustable%2C%20which%20means%20that%20they'll%20be%20accessible%20to%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20body%20types.%20But%20before%20you%20buy%20any%20chair%2C%20check%20the%20specifications%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you'll%20fit%20comfortably%20in%20it%2C%20and%20that%20it'll%20fit%20in%20your%20office%20or%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDoes%20a%20gaming%20chair%20actually%20make%20you%20better%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20complicated%20question%20to%20answer.%20There%20hasn't%20been%20much%20research%20on%20gaming%20chairs%2C%20or%20how%20they%20compare%20to%20other%20sorts%20of%20chairs%20for%20improving%20game%20performance.%20The%20large%20majority%20of%20claims%20about%20gaming%20chairs%20are%20made%20either%20anecdotally%20through%20product%20reviews%20or%20by%20the%20brands%20that%20build%20the%20chairs%20themselves%2C%20neither%20of%20which%20are%20totally%20trustworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20that%20does%20exist%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fieomsociety.org%2Ftoronto2019%2Fpapers%2F18.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%202019%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20De%20La%20Salle%20University's%20School%20of%20Industrial%20Engineering%2C%20suggests%20that%20gaming%20chairs%20do%20improve%20gaming%20performance%2C%20although%20in%20an%20indirect%20way.%20Their%20research%20says%20that%20gaming%20chairs%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20ergonomic%2C%20meaning%20that%20gamers%20can%20play%20for%20longer%20periods%20without%20strain%20%E2%80%94%20so%2C%20over%20an%20extended%20period%2C%20their%20focus%2C%20alertness%2C%20and%20skill%20stay%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20gamers%20in%20other%20chairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20chairs%20are%20built%20in%20specific%20ways%20to%20encourage%20focus.%20The%20Herman%20Miller%20Vantum%2C%20for%20example%2C%20slightly%20tilts%20the%20user%20forward%20so%20they're%20closer%20to%20the%20screen.%20But%20the%20research%20suggests%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20improving%20game%20performance%2C%20being%20comfortable%20is%20the%20most%20important%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-chairs%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696272600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651af4054ff1e300194773cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-chairs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20gaming%20chairs%20are%20durable%2C%20comfortable%2C%20and%20adjustable.%20Our%20favorite%20chairs%20for%20gaming%20come%20from%20brands%20like%20Secretlab%20and%20SteelCase.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wantonelli%40insider.com%20(William%20Antonelli%2CBrendan%20Griffiths%2CSimon%20Hill)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-chairs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Madrid%20Market%20Iberseries%20%26amp%3B%20Platino%20Industria%20Says%20About%20the%20TV%20Business%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696272517000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FOperacion-Barrio-Ingles.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235742387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Expanded%20to%20four%20full%20days%2C%20Madrid%E2%80%99s%20Iberseries%20%26amp%3B%20Platino%20Industria%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20of%20the%20Fundaci%C3%B3n%20Secuoya%20and%20EGEDA%2C%20Spain%E2%80%99s%20large%20rights%20collection%20society%2C%20opens%20its%20doors%20for%20its%20third%20edition%20on%20Tuesday%20Oct.%203%2C%20running%20all%20week%20at%20Madrid%E2%80%99s%20Matadero.%C2%A0%20I%20%26amp%3B%20IP%20is%20a%20market%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20Iberscreenings%20showcase%2C%20and%20ever%20more%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalU