she%20wouldn't%20run%20for%20reelection.%20Now%2C%20she's%20threatening%20to%20leave%20office%20sooner%20than%20expected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mhall%40businessinsider.com%20(Madison%20Hall)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgop-representative-threatened-to-quit-if-debt-commission-isnt-made-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20Only%20Face%20Of%20BJP%20In%20Rajasthan%20Is...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20Ahead%20Of%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20said%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20has%20already%20conceded%20defeat%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20by%20requesting%20him%20not%20to%20scrap%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20started%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20gave%20a%20%26quot%3Bguarantee%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20not%20discontinue%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Chittorgarh%2C%20his%20second%20in%20Rajasthan%20in%20a%20week%2C%20PM%20Modi%20gave%20a%20clear%20indication%20that%20no%20leader%20will%20be%20projected%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%20The%20election%20symbol%20'lotus'%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20candidate%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20his%20address%2C%20PM%20Modi%20inaugurated%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20projects%20worth%20Rs%207%2C200%20crore%20at%20another%20event%20in%20Rajasthan.%20He%20also%20offered%20prayers%20in%20the%20Sanwaliya%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20BJP%20state%20president%20CP%20Joshi%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Rajendra%20Rathore%20and%20Union%20minister%20Arjun%20Meghwal%20were%20among%20the%20leaders%20present%20at%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Gehlot%20had%20recently%20demanded%20that%20Modi%20should%20give%20a%20guarantee%20that%20the%20Congress%20government's%20schemes%20will%20not%20be%20discontinued%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20this%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMr%20Gehlot%20knows%20that%20the%20countdown%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20has%20started.%20He%20in%20a%20way%20has%20congratulated%20the%20BJP%20by%20publicly%20requesting%20that%20welfare%20schemes%20be%20not%20stopped.%20I%20assure%20you%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20not%20stop%20any%20scheme%20of%20public%20interest%20but%20will%20try%20to%20improve%20it.%20This%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee.%26quot%3B%20Later%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20accepted%20that%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20has%20done%20good%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20chief%20minister%20threw%20a%20trap%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20fell%20for%20it%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20Gehlot%20government's%20schemes%20will%20be%20continued.%20When%20our%20schemes%20are%20good%2C%20who%20will%20vote%20for%20you%20(BJP)%2C%26quot%3B%20M%20Khera%20told%20reporters%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Chittorgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20over%20corruption%20and%20women's%20safety%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20it%20pains%20him%20whenever%20atrocities%20take%20place%20against%20daughters%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20Congress%20has%20made%20this%20a%20tradition%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20said%20that%20the%20paper%20leak%20mafia%20in%20Rajasthan%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%20and%20given%20the%20harshest%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20tailor%20Kanhaiya%20Lal's%20brutal%20murder%20in%20Udaipur%20last%20year%2C%20PM%20Modi%20asked%20whether%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20had%20voted%20for%20the%20Congress%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20came%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20getting%20clothes%20stitched%2C%20slit%20the%20throat%20of%20the%20tailor%20without%20any%20fear%20and%20made%20a%20video%20and%20made%20it%20viral.%20The%20Congress%20gets%20worried%20about%20votes%20in%20that%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20alleged%20that%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20celebrate%20any%20festival%20peacefully%20in%20Rajasthan%20because%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-development%26quot%3B%20environment%20created%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20will%20bring%20prosperity%2C%20employment%20and%20development%20to%20the%20state%20besides%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20women%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20claimed%20that%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20by%20lying%20to%20people%20but%20could%20not%20run%20the%20government.%20Chief%20Minister%20Gehlot%20was%20busy%20saving%20his%20chair%20while%20half%20of%20his%20own%20party%20was%20busy%20removing%20him%20for%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20conflicts%20within%20the%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%20but%20they%20had%20consensus%20when%20it%20came%20to%20loot%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20alleged%2C%20adding%20that%20criminals%2C%20rioters%20and%20corrupt%20Congress%20leaders%20considered%20themselves%20the%20government%20and%20such%20a%20dispensation%20should%20not%20last%20even%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRajasthan%20has%20given%20a%20call.%20Will%20save%20Rajasthan%2C%20will%20bring%20BJP%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20further%20said%20that%20after%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20would%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20betrayal%20done%20to%20the%20youths%20of%20Rajasthan.%20%26quot%3BThe%20paper%20leak%20mafia%20here%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%20at%20all%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAction%20will%20definitely%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20have%20committed%20corruption%20here%20and%20looted%20the%20money%20of%20the%20poor.%20This%20is%20also%20Modi's%20guarantee.%20No%20matter%20how%20much%20these%20people%20abuse%20Modi%2C%20strict%20action%20against%20corruption%20will%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20whenever%20the%20Congress%20feels%20it%20is%20going%20to%20lose%20in%20an%20election%2C%20it%20starts%20making%20false%20announcements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20government%20is%20also%20making%20such%20efforts%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20busy%20saving%20the%20government%20and%20now%2C%20it%20is%20worried%20about%20people's%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20comes%20on%20top%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20crime%2C%20PM%20Modi%20claimed.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20anarchy%2C%20riots%20and%20stone-pelting%2C%20the%20name%20of%20Rajasthan%20is%20infamous.%20Today%20our%20Rajasthan%20is%20becoming%20the%20most%20infamous%20in%20cases%20of%20atrocities%20on%20women%2C%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20identity%20of%20Rajasthan%20is%20of%20hospitality%2C%20folk%20music%2C%20folk%20culture%2C%20bravery.%20But%20in%20five%20years%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%20has%20ruined%20the%20credibility%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20saying%20insulting%20things%20about%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20every%20day%20what%20insulting%20things%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20arrogant%20alliance%20of%20the%20Congress%20are%20saying%20about%20women.%20They%20do%20not%20want%20women%20to%20get%20their%20rights%2C%20hence%20they%20are%20making%20excuses%20and%20spreading%20confusion%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20clear%20there%20were%20no%20factions%20in%20the%20BJP's%20state%20leadership%20and%20it%20will%20contest%20the%20election%20under%20the%20party's%20'lotus'%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20the%20symbol%20of%20'lotus'.%20Our%20hope%20and%20candidate%20is%20the%20lotus%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20further%20said%20that%20every%20poor%20of%20the%20country%20would%20get%20a%20permanent%20roof%20to%20live%20in.%20%26quot%3BModi%20will%20give%20a%20permanent%20roof%20to%20every%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20direct%20benefit%20transfer%20(DBT)%20to%20farmers'%20accounts%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20transferred%20lakhs%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20directly%20to%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20beneficiaries.%20PM%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%20comes%20directly%20into%20the%20farmer's%20account.%20Modi's%20model%20is%20the%20same%20%E2%80%93%20direct%20benefits%20to%20every%20beneficiary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696269660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F533d26g8_pm-modi-ani_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-in-rajasthan-the-only-face-of-bjp-in-rajasthan-is-4443302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20said%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20has%20already%20conceded%20defeat%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20by%20requesting%20him%20not%20to%20scrap%20the%20