this%20year.%20He%20had%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20how%20green%20hydrogen%20can%20power%20a%20car.%20At%20the%20launch%2C%20he%20said%20that%20green%20hydrogen%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20efficient%2C%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%20energy%20pathway%20to%20make%20India%20energy%20self-reliant%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitin%20Gadkari%20had%20in%20January%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20himself%20use%20a%20hydrogen-powered%20car.%20%26quot%3BToyota%20Company%20from%20Japan%20has%20given%20me%20a%20vehicle%20which%20runs%20on%20green%20Hydrogen.%20I%20will%20use%20it%20myself%20as%20a%20pilot%20project%20(on%20alternative%20fuel)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitin%20Gadkari%20has%20often%20favoured%20a%20green%20transition%20in%20fuel%2C%20saying%20rapid%20strides%20in%20green%20fuel%20technology%20will%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20bringing%20them%20on%20a%20par%20with%20petrol-run%20vehicles%20in%20two%20years'%20time.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696265880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0ddt2hlg_nitin-gadkari_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-nitin-gadkari-takes-a-test-drive-on-hydrogen-bus-in-prague-4443741%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Transport%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20who%20is%20on%20an%20official%20visit%20to%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20took%20a%20test%20drive%20on%20a%20hydrogen%20bus%20in%20Prague%20today.%20Mr%20Gadkari%2C%20flanked%20by%20several%20officials%2C%20was%20seen%20riding%20the%20bus%2C%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-nitin-gadkari-takes-a-test-drive-on-hydrogen-bus-in-prague-4443741%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-ni