ews%2Fbihar-caste-survey-out-27-backward-classes-36-extremely-backward-classes-4442234%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%2027%25%20Backward%20Classes%2C%2036%25%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20-%20coming%20months%20before%20next%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20-%20underlines%20the%20electoral%20importance%20of%20OBCs%20and%20marginalised%20communities%20-%20both%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20opposed%20calls%20for%20a%20national%20caste%20census%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20has%20been%20increasingly%20more%20and%20more%20vocal%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%20over%20OBC%20votes%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201999%20national%20election%20the%20OBC%20vote%20division%20was%20even%20-%2023%20to%2024%20per%20cent.%20This%20jumped%20to%2034%20per%20cent%20to%2015%20per%20cent%20in%202014%20and%20then%20a%20massive%2044%20per%20cent%20for%20the%20BJP%20five%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-lalu-yadav-bihar-caste-survey-bjp-bihar-caste-survey-results-out-nitish-kumar-shares-the-plan-ahead-4442545%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBihar%20Caste%20Survey%20Results%20Out%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Shares%20The%20Plan%20Ahead%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20that%2063%20per%20cent%20OBC%2B%20EBC%20is%20a%20headline%20number%20for%20the%20BJP.%20In%202019%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20won%2039%20of%20the%20state's%2040%20seats%3B%20the%20BJP%20won%2017%2C%20JDU%20(then%20its%20ally)%2016%20and%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20got%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20then%2C%20benefitted%20from%20OBC%20votes%2C%20as%20they%20did%20in%20the%202020%20Bihar%20election%2C%20when%2081%20per%20cent%20of%20Kurmis%2C%2051%20per%20cent%20of%20Koeris%2C%20and%2058%20per%20cent%20of%20other%20OBCs%2FEBCs%20voted%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERepresentation%2C%20though%2C%20hasn't%20always%20been%20equal%20to%20population%20-%20a%20point%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20made%20when%20he%20said%20only%20three%20of%2090%20Secretaries%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20were%20from%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimportant-to-know-caste-statistics-of-india-says-rahul-gandhi-on-census-4442845%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BImportant%20To%20Know%20Caste%20Statistics%20Of%20India%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20On%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20comparing%20the%202015%20Bihar%20Assembly%20to%20the%202020%20one%20shows%20a%20drop%20in%20MLAs%20from%20OBC%20and%20EBC%20communities%20from%2048.6%20per%20cent%20to%2040.7.%20MLAs%20from%20the%20so-called%20upper%20castes%20increased%20from%2023.9%20per%20cent%20to%2029.2%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20those%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20fell%20from%209.9%20to%207.8%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party-wise%20division%20of%20these%20numbers%20identifies%20the%20BJP%20as%20having%20only%2027%20MLAs%20from%20OBC%20communities%20(compared%20to%2034%20from%20so-called%20upper%20castes).%20For%20the%20JDU%20this%20split%20was%2022-10.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20RJD%20skew%20was%20even%20bigger%20in%20terms%20of%20OBC%20representation%20-%2039-13.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20what%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20report%20also%20does%20is%20spotlight%20the%20significance%20of%20OBC%20%2B%20EBC%20communities%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20all%20political%20parties%20across%20the%20country%2C%20with%20particular%20focus%20on%20states%20voting%20this%20year%20-%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%20OBCs%20(as%20a%20percentage%20of%20households%20in%20rural%20areas)%20account%20for%20over%2057%20per%20cent.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%20that%20number%20is%2051.4%20per%20cent.%20This%20is%2046.8%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%2042.4%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20has%20been%20a%20polarising%20topic%20among%20India's%20political%20parties%2C%20with%20battle%20lines%20drawn%20between%20(primarily)%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20on%20one%20side%20and%20a%20number%20of%20opposition%20parties%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20at%20an%20election%20event%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Gwalior%20today%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20those%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%26quot%3B%20-%20seen%20as%20a%20sharp%20response%20to%20Bihar's%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-caste-census-pm-modi-trying-to-divide-country-pm-after-bihar-releases-caste-survey-report-4443232%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTrying%20To%20Divide%20Country...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20After%20Bihar%20Releases%20Caste%20Survey%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20is%20pushing%20for%20a%20national%20caste%20census%20to%20ensure%20better%20targeting%20of%20development%20initiatives%2C%20has%20been%20boosted%20by%20the%20Bihar%20report.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20-%20whose%20Congress%20is%20part%20of%20INDIA%20-%20said%20his%20party%20will%20order%20a%20similar%20exercise%20if%20it%20wins%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20election%20due%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696265580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fc545oumc_nitish-kumar-1200_625x300_16_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-caste-based-survey-ndtv-explains-4443519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NDTV%20explains%20after%20the%20Bihar%20governm