wn%20self-image%20are%20on%20the%20line%2C%20but%20he%20calls%20the%20case%20a%20sham.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A839%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66987215%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66987215.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66987215.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Seattle%2C%20Fresno%20Becomes%20Second%20US%20City%20to%20Ban%20Caste%20Discrimination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F22121433%2FFph8kZ-aIAApPPD.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFresno%20in%20California%20has%20become%20the%20second%20city%20in%20the%20United%20States%20to%20ban%20caste%20discrimination%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fseattle-now-the-first-us-city-to-have-banned-caste-discrimination%5C%22%3ESeattle%3C%2Fa%3E%20outlawed%20it%20in%20September%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20unanimously%20passed%20Bill%20by%20the%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20on%20Thursday%2C%20September%2028%2C%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20caste%20discrimination%20faced%20by%20people%20of%20South%20Asian%20descent%20and%20%3Cem%3Ecasta%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Oaxacans%20from%20Mexico.%20Casta%2C%20a%20hierarchical%20social%20order%2C%20is%20analogous%20to%20the%20caste-based%20hierarchies%20practiced%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Sikhs%20along%20with%20Oaxacans%20have%20led%20the%20movement%20to%20outlaw%20caste%20discrimination.%20The%20two%20communities%20have%20been%20farmers%20or%20farm%20workers%20for%20years%20in%20Fresno%20County%20and%20Central%20Valley%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ELos%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-09-30%2Fin-fresno-sikhs-and-oaxacans-unite-to-pass-caste-discrimination-ban%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20had%20picked%20up%20steam%20since%20October%202022%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flos-angeles-council-president-steps-down-after-audio-leak-racist-comments-2022-10-10%2F%5C%22%3Eleaked%20audio%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%202022%20in%20which%20three%20Los%20Angeles%20City%20Council%20members%20were%20heard%20making%20racist%20comments%20against%20Oaxacans.%20The%20incident%2C%20which%20outraged%20the%20members%20of%20the%20civil%20rights%20movement%20in%20the%20US%2C%20has%20also%20drawn%20renewed%20attention%20to%20the%20discrimination%20faced%20by%20Oaxacans%2C%20due%20to%20the%20casta%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20proud%20of%20our%20City%20for%20once%20again%2C%20raising%20the%20bar%20on%20civil%20rights%20protections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20vice-president%20Annalisa%20Perea%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffresno-in-california-becomes-second-us-city-to-ban-caste-discrimination-101696185015475.html%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20television%20network.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20acknowledge%20that%20discrimination%20won%E2%80%99t%20end%20overnight%2C%20our%20City%20took%20bold%20action%20by%20passing%20this%20anti-discrimination%20policy%20to%20strengthen%20civil%20rights%20protections%20against%20caste%20discrimination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mexico%20was%20colonised%20by%20Spain%2C%20a%20system%20called%C2%A0%3Ci%3ESistema%20de%20Castas%20%3C%2Fi%3Ewas%20established.%20According%20to%20this%2C%20those%20born%20in%20Spain%20as%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cpure%20Spaniards%E2%80%9D%2C%20placed%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hierarchial%20order%2C%20followed%20by%20Spaniards%20born%20in%20Mexico.%20Oaxacans%2C%20who%20are%20indigenous%20peoples%2C%20are%20placed%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20hierarchical%20order%20alongside%20Blacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20colonial%20period%2C%20the%20Spaniards%20implemented%20this%20system%20that%20resembled%20very%20much%20the%20system%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ELA%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-09-30%2Fin-fresno-sikhs-and-oaxacans-unite-to-pass-caste-discrimination-ban%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gaspar%20Rivera-Salgado%20as%20saying.%20Rivera-Salgado%2C%20an%20Oaxacan%20American%2C%20is%20the%20director%20Center%20for%20Mexican%20Studies%20at%20UCLA%20and%20a%20board%20member%20at%20the%20Binational%20Center%20for%20the%20Development%20of%20Oaxacan%20Indigenous%20Communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESikhs%20in%20Fresno%20saw%20in%20the%20plight%20of%20Oaxacans%2C%20the%20discrimination%20and%20oppression%20faced%20by%20the%20members%20of%20lower%20castes%20from%20South%20Asia.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20groups%20have%20shared%20a%20common%20experience%20of%20inequity%20and%20being%20treated%20as%20less%20than%2C%20right%20away%20they%20can%20understand%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20pain%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ELA%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Deep%20Singh%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Jakara%20Movement%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20is%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20larger%20movement%20advocating%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20caste%20discrimination%20across%20California%20state.%20Although%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcalifornia-legislature-passes-anti-caste-discrimination-bill%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMarch%252023%252C%25202023.%2Con%2520Monday%2520(August%252028).%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20Senate%3C%2Fa%3E%20passed%20a%20Bill%20with%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20outlawing%20caste%20in%20May%20this%20year%2C%20it%20is%20still%20pending%20for%20an%20approval%20from%20governor%20Gavin%20Newsom.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20rights%E2%80%99%20bodies%20have%20been%20exerting%20pressure%20on%20Newsom%20to%20sign%20the%20Bill%20in%20order%20to%20make%20it%20a%20law.%20Thenmozhi%20Soundararajan%2C%20an%20Indian%20American%20Dalit%20rights%20activist%2C%20has%20been%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%20for%20about%20a%20month%20demanding%20Newsom%20approve%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hindu%20nationalist%20groups%20in%20America%20have%20been%20opposing%20the%20latest%20Bill%20passed%20by%20the%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20and%20the%20movement%20and%20groups%20calling%20for%20laws%20at%20the%20federal%20level%20to%20identify%20and%20ban%20caste%20discrimination.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20such%20laws%20would%20%E2%80%9Csingle%20out%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hindu%20community%20as%20perpetrators%20of%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696265321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F22121433%2FFph8kZ-aIAApPPD.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fafter-seattle-fresno-becomes-second-us-city-to-ban-caste-discrimination%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Sikhs%20along%20with%20Oaxacans%20led%20the%20movement%20that%20eventually%20prompted%20the%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20to%20unanimously%20pass%20the%20Bill%20to%20outlaw%20caste.%20Oaxacans%20from%20Mexico%20are%20placed%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20'casta'%20hierarchical%20order%2C%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20caste%20system%20practiced%20in%20South%20Asia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fafter-seattle-fresno-becomes-second-us-city-to-ban-caste-discrimination%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSham%2C%20Horrow%20Show%26quot%3B%3A%20Trump%20As%20Civil%20Fraud%20Trial%20In%20New%20York%20Begins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20civil%20fraud%20trial%20that%20could%20deal%20a%20major%20blow%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%20real%20estate%20empire%20began%20on%20Monday%2C%20with%20a%20New%20York%20state%20lawyer%20accusing%20the%20former%20president%20of%20generating%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20by%20lying%2C%20and%20Trump%20blasting%20the%20case%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bscam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20in%20a%20downtown%20Manhattan%20courtroom%20case%20concerns%20accusations%20by%20state%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20that%20Trump%20inflated%20his%20assets%20and%20his%20own%20net%20worth%20from%202011%20to%202021%20to%20obtain%20favorable%20bank%20loans%20and%20lower%20insurance%20premiums.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJames%20is%20seeking%20at%20least%20%24250%20million%20in%20fines%2C%20a%20permanent%20ban%20against%20Trump%20and%20his%20sons%20Donald%20Jr%20and%20Eric%20from%20running%20businesses%20in%20New%20York%20and%20a%20five-year%20commercial%20real%20estate%20ban%20against%20Trump%20and%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20looked%20on%20with%20his%20arms%20crossed%20are%20Kevin%20Wallace%2C%20a%20lawyer%20in%20James'%20office%2C%20called%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bmaterially%20inaccurate%26quot%3B%20in%20describing%20his%20finances%20to%20banks%20and%20insurers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20business%20as%20usual%2C%20and%20this%20isn't%20how%20sophisticated%20parties%20deal%20with%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Wallace%20said%20in%20his%20opening%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20victimless%20crimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Kise%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Trump%2C%20countered%20in%20his%20opening%20statement%20that%20the%20financials%20for%20Trump%20and%20the%20Trump%20organization%20were%20entirely%20legal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20highly%20successful%20brands%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20he%20has%20made%20a%20fortune%20literally%20being%20right%20about%20real%20estate%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20Kise%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20intent%20to%20defraud%2C%20there%20was%20no%20illegality%2C%20there%20was%20no%20default%2C%20there%20was%20no%20breach%2C%20there%20was%20no%20reliance%20from%20the%20banks%2C%20there%20were%20no%20unjust%20profits%2C%20and%20there%20were%20no%20victims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20holds%20a%20commanding%20lead%20over%20rivals%20for%20the%202024%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20wore%20a%20dark%20blue%20suit%2C%20a%20brighter%20blue%20tie%20and%20an%20American%20flag%20pin%20on%20his%20lapel%2C%20and%20told%20reporters%20before%20entering%20the%20courtroom%20that%20the%20case%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bscam%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%26quot%3Bsham%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20continuation%20of%20the%20single%20greatest%20witch%20hunt%20of%20all%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20great%20company.%20I%20built%20a%20great%20company.%20It's%20tremendous%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20got%20some%20of%20the%20greatest%20real%20estate%20assets%20in%20the%20world.%20And%20now%20I%20have%20to%20go%20in%20before%20a%20rogue%20judge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJames%20said%20her%20office%20was%20ready%20to%20prove%20its%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20law%20is%20both%20powerful%20and%20fragile%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20before%20entering%20the%20courtroom.%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20much%20money%20you%20think%20you%20may%20have%2C%20no%20one%20is%20above%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump's%20trial%20is%20overseen%20by%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron%2C%20who%20will%20hear%20evidence%20without%20a%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20largely%20concerns%20penalties%20that%20Trump%2C%20his%20adult%20sons%20and%2010%20of%20his%20companies%20must%20face%20after%20Engoron%20last%20week%20found%20them%20liable%20for%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20opening%20arguments%2C%20Engoron%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20generalist%20on%20the%20law.%20%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20I%20know%20a%20lot%20about%20is%20the%20definition%20of%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20Sept.%2026%20decision%2C%20Engoron%20described%20in%20scathing%20terms%20how%20the%20defendants%20made%20up%20valuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20included%20Trump%20calculating%20the%20value%20of%20his%20apartment%20in%20Trump%20Tower%20as%20if%20it%20were%20three%20times%20its%20actual%20size%2C%20and%20listing%20his%20Mar-a-Lago%20estate%20as%20being%20worth%20up%20to%20%24739%20million%20though%20deed%20restrictions%20capped%20it%20at%20%2428%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngoron's%20decision%20also%20covers%20several%20other%20properties%20including%20Trump's%20family%20estate%20in%20Westchester%20County%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20various%20office%20buildings%20and%20golf%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20canceled%20business%20certificates%20for%20companies%20controlling%20pillars%20of%20Trump's%20empire%2C%20and%20said%20he%20would%20appoint%20receivers%20to%20oversee%20their%20dissolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20responded%20to%20the%20decision%20by%20calling%20Engoron%20%26quot%3Bderanged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWallace%20played%20an%20excerpt%20from%20a%20deposition%20where%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20who%20had%20been%20Trump's%20personal%20lawyer%20and%20fixer%20but%20has%20since%20turned%20against%20his%20former%20boss%2C%20said%20the%20goal%20was%20%26quot%3Bto%20attain%20the%20number%20that%20Mr.%20Trump%20wanted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKise%20countered%20that%20just%20because%20people%20disagree%20about%20valuations%20does%20not%20mean%20one%20valuation%20must%20be%20fraudulent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20Trump's%20banks%20and%20insurers%20knew%20his%20valuations%20were%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20designed%20to%20be%20absolutes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20is%20scheduled%20to%20run%20through%20early%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20150%20people%20including%20Cohen%20could%20testify%2C%20though%20much%20of%20the%20trial%20may%20be%20a%20battle%20of%20experts%20opining%20on%20financial%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20faces%20several%20other%20legal%20headaches%2C%20which%20have%20been%20a%20financial%20drain%2C%20and%20made%20him%20the%20first%20sitting%20or%20former%20U.S.%20president%20to%20be%20criminally%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20criminally%20charged%20in%20Washington%20over%20his%20efforts%20to%20undo%20his%20loss%20in%20the%202020%20presidential%20election%2C%20in%20Georgia%20over%20moves%20to%20reverse%20election%20results%20there%2C%20in%20Florida%20over%20his%20handling%20of%20classified%20documents%20upon%20leaving%20office%2C%20and%20in%20New%20York%20over%20hush%20money%20payments%20to%20a%20porn%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20denied%20all%20wrongdoing%20and%20pleaded%20not%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696265160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fhsts6clo_donald-trump_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsham-horrow-show-trump-as-civil-fraud-trial-in-new-york-begins-4443459%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20said%20his%20civil%20fraud%20trial%20starting%20in%20New%20York%20Monday%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsham%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20the%20state%20attorney%20general%20who%20brought%20the%20case%20a%20%26quot%3Bhorror%20show.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsham-horrow-show-trump-as-civil-fraud-trial-in-new-york-begins-4443459%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsham-horrow-show-trump-as-civil-fraud-trial-in-new-york-begins-444345