20In%20Maharashtra%20Hospital%20In%20A%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwelve%20newborns%20and%20as%20many%20adults%20died%20at%20a%20state-run%20hospital%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Nanded%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours%2C%20the%20hospital%20dean%20said%2C%20blaming%20a%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20and%20hospital%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%2024%20deaths%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours%2C%2012%20adults%20were%20suffering%20from%20%26quot%3Bvarious%20ailments%2C%20mostly%20snake%20bites%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20dean%20of%20Nanded's%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%20Government%20Hospital%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSix%20males%20and%20six%20female%20babies%20died%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours.%20Twelve%20adults%20also%20died%20due%20to%20various%20ailments%2C%20mostly%20snake%20bites.%20We%20faced%20some%20difficulty%20since%20various%20staff%20were%20being%20transferred%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20a%20tertiary-level%20care%20centre%20and%20the%20only%20such%20place%20in%20the%2070%20to%2080-km%20radius.%20So%2C%20patients%20come%20to%20us%20from%20far-off%20places.%20On%20some%20days%2C%20the%20number%20of%20patients%20increases%20and%20it%20creates%20a%20problem%20for%20the%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fina1cnp8_nanded-hospital-1200_650x400_02_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20institute%20Haffkine.%20We%20are%20supposed%20to%20buy%20medicines%20from%20them%20but%20that%20also%20didn't%20happen.%20But%20we%20did%20buy%20medicines%20locally%20and%20provided%20them%20to%20the%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20dean%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERefuting%20the%20dean's%20claims%20that%20there%20was%20a%20shortage%20of%20medicine%20and%20funds%2C%20the%20hospital%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BEssential%20medicines%20are%20available%20in%20the%20hospital.%20The%20hospital%20has%20Rs%2012%20crore%20in%20funds.%20For%20this%20financial%20year%2C%20Rs%204%20crore%20has%20been%20approved.%20Other%20patients%20are%20being%20treated%20as%20necessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%2012%20adult%20patients%20(five%20male%20and%20seven%20female)%20and%2012%20children.%20Among%20adults%2C%20four%20were%20suffering%20from%20heart%20disease%2C%20one%20from%20poisoning%2C%20one%20from%20gastric%20disease%2C%20two%20from%20kidney%20ailments%2C%20one%20from%20obstetric%20complications%2C%20and%20three%20were%20accident%20victims.%20Among%20the%20children%2C%20four%20in%20the%20terminal%20stage%20were%20referred%20from%20private%20hospitals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20deaths%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20told%20reporters%20in%20Mumbai%20that%20more%20information%20will%20be%20sought%20about%20what%20happened%20at%20the%20hospital%20and%20action%20will%20be%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20committee%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20deaths%2C%20Dr%20Dilip%20Mhaisekar%2C%20Director%2C%20Medical%20Education%20and%20Research%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20told%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20three-member%20expert%20committee%20from%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20(formerly%20Aurangabad)%20district%20has%20been%20formed%20with%20a%20mandate%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20by%201%20pm%20tomorrow.%20I%20am%20personally%20visiting%20the%20hospital%20to%20review%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20in%20Maharashtra%20launched%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20saying%20the%20%26quot%3Btriple-engine%20sarkar%20(of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde%20Sena%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20NCP)%20should%20take%20responsibility%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20total%20of%2024%20lives%20were%20lost.%20Seventy%20are%20still%20critical.%20There%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20medical%20facilities%20and%20staff.%20Many%20nurses%20were%20transferred%20and%20their%20replacements%20were%20not%20given.%20Many%20machines%20are%20not%20working.%20The%20hospital's%20capacity%20is%20500%2C%20but%201%2C200%20patients%20are%20admitted.%20I%20will%20speak%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar%20(about%20this).%20The%20government%20should%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20keenly%20and%20take%20control%20of%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20veteran%20Ashok%20Chavan%20said%20after%20visiting%20the%20hospital%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20triple-engine%20sarkar%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20all%20the%2024%20innocent%20people.%20They%20should%20be%20made%20accountable%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B24%20deaths%2C%20which%20include%2012%20newborn%20babies%2C%20in%2024%20hours%20in%20the%20government%20hospital%20in%20Nanded%20happened%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20supply%20of%20medicine%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20Shame%20on%20a%20government%20that%20only%20advertises%20festivals%20and%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%2C%20Vikas%20Lawande%2C%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20less%20than%20two%20months%20after%2018%20patients%20died%20in%2024%20hours%20in%20August%20at%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20Hospital%20in%20Kalwa%20in%20Thane.%20Twelve%20of%20them%20were%20above%20the%20age%20of%2050.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20patients%20were%20suffering%20from%20complications%20due%20to%20kidney%20stones%2C%20chronic%20paralysis%2C%20ulcers%2C%20pneumonia%2C%20kerosene%20poisoning%2C%20and%20septicemia%20among%20other%20ailments%2C%20Thane%20civic%20commissioner%20Abhijit%20Bangar%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20deaths%2C%20Authorities%20shifted%20patients%2C%20who%20were%20not%20in%20critical%20and%20all%20new%20admissions%2C%20to%20the%20Civil%20Hospital%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696263300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0gumjs4_nanded-hospital_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F24-patients-including-12-newborns-die-in-maharashtra-hospital-in-a-day-official-cites-shortage-of-medicines-4443370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twelve%20newborns%20and%20as%20many%20adults%20died%20at%20a%20state-run%20hospital%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Nanded%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours%2C%20the%20hospital%20dean%20said%2C%20blaming%20a%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20and%20hospital%20staff.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F24-patients-including-12-newborns-die-in-maharashtra-hospital-in-a-day-official-cites-shortage-of-medicines-4443370%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F24-patients-including-12-newborns-die-in-maharashtra-hospital-in-a-day-official-cites-shortage-of-medicines-4443370%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F24-patients-including-12-newborns-die-in-maharashtra-hospital-in-a-day-official-cites-shortage-of-medicines-4443370%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20world%E2%80%99s%20costliest%20weapons%20program%20just%20got%20more%20expensive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696263004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104112020%2Cimgsize-47384.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fuss-f-35-fighter-jet-worlds-costliest-weapons-program-just-got-more-expensive%2Farticleshow%2F104111995.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cost%20of%20the%20US's%20F-35