l%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104111803%2Cimgsize-1044864.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fcivil-fraud-case-trump-gave-inaccurate-financial-information-says-lawyer%2Farticleshow%2F104111770.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20appeared%20in%20a%20state%20court%20in%20New%20York%20for%20a%20civil%20fraud%20case%20involving%20him%20and%20his%20family%20business.%20The%20case%20alleges%20that%20Trump%20provided%20inaccurate%20financial%20information%20to%20banks%20and%20insurers%20and%20lied%20about%20his%20assets%20to%20obtain%20better%20loan%20and%20insurance%20terms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Jupiter-Sized'%20Objects%20Seen%20Free-Floating%20In%20Space%2C%20Astronomers%20Clueless%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20James%20Webb%20Space%20Telescope%20(JWST)%2C%20the%20most%20powerful%20telescope%20developed%20by%20mankind%2C%20has%20spotted%20Jupiter-sized%20''planets''%20that%20are%20free-floating%20in%20space%20and%20not%20connected%20to%20any%20star%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-66974738%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20These%20objects%20have%20been%20nicknamed%20Jupiter%20Mass%20Binary%20Objects%2C%20or%20''JuMBOs''.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%2040%20pairs%20of%20these%20were%20identified%20by%20the%20JWST%20during%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20Orion%20Nebula.%20Notably%2C%20these%20objects%20are%20too%20small%20to%20be%20stars%2C%20but%20also%20defy%20the%20conventional%20definition%20of%20a%20planet%20because%20they%20are%20not%20in%20orbit%20around%20a%20parent%20star.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20these%20mysterious%20objects%20have%20left%20astronomers%20clueless%20who%20are%20struggling%20to%20explain%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENew%20space%20images!%F0%9F%A4%A9%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20The%20NASA%2FESA%2FCSA%20James%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWebb%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Webb%3C%2Fa%3E%20Space%20Telescope%20has%20added%20detailed%20images%20of%20the%20Orion%20Nebula%20to%20our%20ESASky%20application.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Zoom%20into%20this%20region%20with%20a%20rich%20diversity%20of%20phenomena%20including%20protostars%2C%20brown%20dwarfs%20and%20even%20free-floating%20planets!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIn4FQk8hrX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIn4FQk8hrX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20ESA%20(%40esa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fesa%2Fstatus%2F1708787072788504816%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Space%20Agency%20(ESA)%20team%20has%20given%20two%20possible%20origin%20explanations%20for%20these%20massive%20objects.%20The%20first%20one%20is%20that%20these%20objects%20grew%20out%20of%20regions%20in%20the%20nebula%20where%20the%20density%20of%20material%20was%20insufficient%20to%20make%20fully-fledged%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20possibility%20is%20that%20they%20are%20planets%20that%20formed%20around%20stars%20but%20were%20eventually%20%E2%80%98kicked%20out'%20due%20to%20gravitational%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''The%20ejection%20hypothesis%20is%20the%20favoured%20one%20at%20the%20moment.%20Gas%20physics%20suggests%20you%20shouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20make%20objects%20with%20the%20mass%20of%20Jupiter%20on%20their%20own%2C%20and%20we%20know%20single%20planets%20can%20get%20kicked%20out%20from%20star%20systems.%20But%20how%20do%20you%20kick%20out%20pairs%20of%20these%20things%20together%3F%20Right%20now%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20an%20answer.%20It's%20one%20for%20the%20theoreticians%2C''%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency's%20(Esa)%20senior%20science%20adviser%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-66974738%5C%22%3EBBC%20News.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2023%2F10%2F02%2Fjames-webb-space-telescopes-images-pairs-of-wandering-planets-19590824%2F%5C%22%3EMetro.co.uk%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dr%20Ed%20Bloomer%2C%20astronomer%20at%20Royal%20Observatory%20Greenwich%20said%2C%20''It's%20happening%20in%20the%20Orion%20Nebula%2C%20a%20star-forming%20%E2%80%98stellar%20nursery'%20where%20we%20have%20already%20seen%20hundreds%20of%20nascent%20planetary%20systems.%20Together%2C%20this%20points%20to%20the%20possibility%20that%20our%20existing%20models%20and%20explanations%20for%20planetary%20formation%20and%20evolution%20aren't%20as%20complete%20as%20we'd%20like%20them%20to%20be%20%E2%80%93%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20any%20astronomer%20would%20claim%20that%20we%20had%20explained%20everything%20in%20that%20area%20of%20astrophysics%20anyway.%C2%A0Potentially%20we're%20looking%20at%20something%20very%20different%20from%20what%20anyone%20has%20seen%20before.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Webb%20telescope%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20in%202021%20and%20began%20collecting%20data%20in%202022%2C%20has%20reshaped%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20early%20universe%20while%20taking%20stunning%20pictures%20of%20the%20cosmos.%C2%A0Since%20becoming%20operational%2C%20Webb%20has%20revealed%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20earliest-known%20galaxies%2C%20and%20black%20holes%2C%20and%20unleashed%20a%20raft%20of%20unprecedented%20data.%C2%A0Webb%20is%20about%20100%20times%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20Hubble%20telescope.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696261680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Feg6imkr8_-jupitersized-objects-floating-in-space_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fjames-webb-telescope-spots-jupiter-sized-objects-floating-in-space-astronomers-clueless-4443546%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Around%2040%20pairs%20of%20these%20objects%20were%20identified%20by%20the%20James%20Webb%20Space%20Telescope%20during%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20Orion%20Nebula.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fjames-webb-telescope-spots-jupiter-sized-objects-floating-in-space-astronomers-clueless-4443546%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fjames-webb-telescope-spots-jupiter-sized-objects-floating-in-space-astronomers-clueless-4443546%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fjames-webb-telescope-spots-jupiter-sized-objects-floating-in-space-astronomers-clueless-4443546%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20nurses%20tied%20Sikh%20patient's%20beard%20with%20plastic%20gloves%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696261171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104111782%2Cimgsize-594296.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fnri%2Fother-news%2Fuk-nurses-tied-sikh-patients-beard-with-plastic-gloves-left-him-in-urine-gave-him-food-he-couldnt-eat-media-report%2Farticleshow%2F104111723.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104111723.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENurses%20in%20the%20UK%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20subjecting%20a%20Sikh%20patient%20to%20%26quot%3Binstitutional%20racism%26quot%3B%20after%20reportedly%20tying%20his%20beard%20with%20plastic%20gloves%2C%20leaving%20him%20in%20his%20own%20urine%2C%20and%20offering%20him%20food%20he%20couldn't%20eat%20for%20religious%20reasons.%20The%20incident%20was%20revealed%20in%20a%20leaked%20dossier%20from%20the%20Nursing%20and%20Midwifery%20Council%20(NMC)%2C%20which%20outlines%20multiple%20cases%20of%20alleged%20racism%20against%20nursing%20staff%20and%20patients.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fnri%2Fother-news%2Fuk-nurses-tied-sikh-patients-beard-with-plastic-gloves-left-him-in-urine-gave-him-food-he-couldnt-eat-media-report%2Farticleshow%2F104111723.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fnri%2Fother-news%2Fuk-nurses-tied-sikh-patients-beard-with-plastic-gloves-left-him-in-urine-gave-him-food-he-couldnt-eat-media-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F104111723.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fnri%2Fother-news%2Fuk-nurses-tied-sikh-patients-beard-with-plastic-gloves-left-him-in-urine-gave-him-food-he-couldnt-eat-media-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F104111723.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Caste%20Census%20Pitch%20Game%20Changer%20In%20Hindi%20Heartland%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESince%202014%20we%20have%20seen%20how%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20consolidated%20its%20hold%20over%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%20We%20see%20the%20BJP%20win%20every%20single%20seat%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20that%20too%20twice%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThings%20are%20better%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20regional%20parties%20in%20state%20elections%20but%20only%20relatively.%20The%20BJP's%20dominance%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20rests%20on%20its%20consolidation%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20or%20OBCs%2C%20particularly%20the%20lower%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20that%20the%20BJP's%20popular%20face%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20is%20also%20from%20a%20lower%20OBC%20community.%20Along%20with%20dogged%20booth-level%20engagement%20of%20OBCs%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20managed%20to%20consolidate%20what%20used%20to%20be%20a%20fragmented%20caste%20group.%20Lower%20OBCs%2C%20often%20small%20and%20fragmented%2C%20used%20to%20be%20the%20ultimate%20swing%20voters.%20These%20were%20the%20voters%20who%20would%20change%20governments%2C%20as%20votes%20like%20Muslims%2C%20upper%20castes%20and%20Dalits%20tend%20to%20have%20strong%20party%20and%20ideological%20affiliations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20opposition%20and%20particular%20the%20Congress%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20move%20the%20lower%20OBC%20vote.%20In%20close%20contests%20even%20a%20slight%20shift%20of%20this%20vote%20can%20shift%20seats%20from%20BJP%20to%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20pitch%20of%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20greater%20representation%20of%20OBCs%20is%20a%20game%20changer.%20You%20will%20see%20the%20impact%20as%20early%20as%20this%20December%2C%20in%20the%20results%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkrupepg_rahul-gandhi-_625x300_26_September_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETurning%20The%20Page%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20has%20effectively%20buried%20any%20hesitation%20the%20Congress%20ever%20had%20about%20identifying%20itself%20as%20an%20OBC%20party.%20He%20has%20rightly%20pointed%20out%20that%20three%20out%20of%20our%20Congress%20chief%20ministers%20today%20are%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20caste%20groups%20demand%20greater%20representation%20in%20almost%20every%20state.%20There%20are%20agitations%20which%20sometimes%20turn%20violent.%20Today's%20OBC%20is%20empowered%20with%20smartphones%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20history.%20The%2050%20per%20cent%20limit%20for%20total%20reservations%20is%20getting%20a%20pushback%20from%20state%20after%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20hence%20become%20important%20to%20have%20accurate%20and%20current%20data%20about%20caste%20demography.%20The%20last%20official%20caste%20census%20was%20in%201931.%20In%202023%2C%20caste%20census%20is%20an%20idea%20whose%20time%20has%20come.%20Bihar%20has%20just%20show%20it%20is%20easy%20and%20possible.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20therefore%20caught%20on%20to%20the%20right%20issue%20at%20the%20right%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20Bihar%20data%20will%20make%20it%20apparent%20to%20OBC%20youth%20across%20India%20how%20they%20can%20benefit%20from%20caste%20census.%20It%20bolsters%20their%20demand%20for%20breaking%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20ceiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20has%20further%20attacked%20the%20BJP%20for%20limiting%20their%20OBC%20push%20to%20tokenism.%20He%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20top%20echelons%20of%20the%20bureaucracy%20are%20dominated%20by%20upper%20castes%2C%20and%20that%20women's%20reservations%20in%20assemblies%20should%20have%20OBC%20reservations%20within%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20good%20caste%20census%20will%20give%20us%20clarity%20not%20just%20about%20caste%20demography%20but%20also%20the%20economic%20status%20of%20various%20castes.%20This%20has%20further%20potential%20for%20both%20social%20justice%20and%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fl105ev4_rahul-gandhi-bharat-jodo-yatra-kashmir-twitter-650_650x400_27_January_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWooing%20OBC%20Youth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2090s%20the%20Congress%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20process%20of%20Mandalisation%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20caste%20census%20pitch%20can%20turn%20a%20weakness%20of%20the%20Congress%20into%20a%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECaste%20census%20data%20can%20reveal%20how%20well%20or%20how%20badly%20a%20community%20is%20doing.%20This%20will%20lead%20to%20valid%20and%20just%20demands%20to%20increase%20and%20decrease%20the%20quotas%20through%20sub-categorisation.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20the%20Congress%20can%20firmly%20ally%20itself%20with%20lower%20OBCs%2C%20who%20have%20seemed%20to%20be%20attached%20to%20the%20BJP%20with%20Fevicol%20ka%20jod.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20consolidated%20the%20Congress%20party's%20hold%20over%20its%20own%20core%20voters%2C%20the%20caste%20census%20pitch%20can%20bring%20it%20new%20votes.%20Even%20a%202-3%20per%20cent%20vote%20shift%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20Congress%20on%20this%20account%20could%20make%20electoral%20politics%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20a%20less%20one-sided%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20potential%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20pitch%20goes%20beyond%20its%20contest%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Even%20regional%20parties%20will%20be%20worried%20about%20the%20Congress%20expanding%20into%20their%20vote%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20consistently%20backing%20caste%20census%20and%20greater%20OBC%20representation%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20showing%20the%20way%20for%20expanding%20the%20Congress%20party's%20national%20vote-share%2C%20which%20has%20been%20stable%20at%2019-20%20per%20cent%20since%202014.%20With%20unemployment%20as%20the%20biggest%20concern%20for%20Indian%20youth%2C%20unemployed%20OBC%20youth%20will%20see%20new%20opportunities%20opening%20up%20for%20them%20through%20an%20increase%20in%20OBC%20representation.%20This%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20attract%20new%20youth%20votes%20towards%20the%20Congress%20-%20even%20first%20time%20voters.%20This%20is%20a%20segment%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20particularly%20strong%20with%20PM%20Modi's%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20BJP's%20discomfort%20with%20the%20caste%20census%20issue%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20may%20just%20have%20found%20his%20own%20'polarisation'%20to%20take%20them%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENaresh%20Arora%20is%20Co-founder%20of%20DesignBoxed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696261140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkrupepg_rahul-gandhi-_625x300_26_September_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-caste-census-pitch-game-changer-in-hindi-heartland-4443565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%202014%20we%20have%20seen%20how%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20consolidated%20its%20hold%20over%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%20We%20see%20the%20BJP%20win%20every%20single%20seat%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20that%20too%20twice%20in%20a%20row.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-caste-census-pitch-game-changer-in-hindi-heartland-4443565%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-caste-census-pitch-game-changer-in-hindi-heartland-4443565%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhis-caste-census-pitch-game-changer-in-hindi-heartland-4443565%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UEFA%20vice%20president%20'sorry'%20after%20voting%20for%20Russia's%20football%20return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696260240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-karl-erik-nilsson-uefa_6306512.jpg%3F20231002172239%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fuefa-vice-president-sorry