20caste%20survey%20conducted%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20in%20Bihar%20is%2027.13%25%20and%20that%20of%C2%A0%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBC)%20is%2036.01%25.%20Castes%20like%20Yadav%2C%20Kurmi%2C%20Kushwaha%2C%20etc.%2C%20are%20enumerated%20under%20the%20OBC%20category.%20Together%20OBC-EBC%20groups%20account%20for%2063%25%20of%20the%20state%20population.%20From%20the%20last%20caste%20census%20conducted%20in%201931%20by%20the%20British%2C%20the%20population%20of%20OBC-EBC%20groups%20has%20seen%20a%2010%25%20jump.%20It%20maybe%20noted%20that%20the%201931%20census%20was%20conducted%20in%20the%20then%20undivided%20India%2C%20including%20present-day%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20population%20of%20Yadavs%20is%20the%20highest%20among%20OBC%20castes%20in%20the%20state%20at%2014.26%25%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20core%20vote%20bank%20of%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD).%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Kushwaha%20caste%20is%204.21%25%20and%20that%20of%20the%20Kurmi%20is%202.87%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStatistics%20show%20that%20the%20population%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%20Bihar%20is%2019.65%25%20and%20that%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20is%201.68%25.%C2%A0The%20population%20of%20general%20or%20upper%20caste%20groups%20has%20come%20out%20to%20be%2015.52%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20upper%20castes%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Brahmins%20is%20the%20highest%20at%203.65%25.%20The%20population%20of%20Rajputs%20stands%20at%203.45%25%20and%20the%20Bhumihars%20population%20at%202.86%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCaste%20census%20was%20approved%20by%20all%20parties.%20It%20has%20not%20only%20revealed%20the%20population%20of%20castes%20but%20also%20their%20economic%20conditions.%20On%20this%20basis%2C%20further%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20for%20the%20development%20and%20upliftment%20of%20all%20sections%2C%E2%80%9D%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20and%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20welcomed%20the%20data%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Caste%20Census%20of%20Bihar%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%2C%20and%20ST%20constitute%2084%25%20of%20its%20population.%20Out%20of%2090%20secretaries%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%20only%20three%20are%20OBC%2C%20who%20handle%20only%205%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20budget.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20know%20the%20caste%20statistics%20of%20India.%20The%20greater%20the%20population%2C%20the%20greater%20the%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20RJD%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%20since%20it%20was%20in%20opposition.%20Chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20been%20on%20the%20same%20path.%20Four%20years%20ago%2C%20on%20February%2018%2C%202019%2C%20the%20proposal%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Legislature%2C%20when%20JDU%20and%20BJP%20were%20together.%20RJD%20and%20JDU%20were%20demanding%20caste-based%20enumeration%20in%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20had%20also%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20reaction%20on%20this%2C%20so%20caste%20enumeration%20was%20done%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20decision%20was%20taken.%20Meanwhile%2C%20JDU%20left%20the%20BJP%20and%20formed%20the%20government%20with%20RJD%20and%20caste%20census%20process%20were%20fastened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20of%20the%20caste%20census%20started%20on%20April%2015%20this%20year%20and%20all%20the%20data%20was%20collected%20on%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCaste%20enumeration%20was%20done%20in%20two%20phases%2C%20in%20which%20house%20listing%20was%20done%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20and%20caste%20enumeration%20of%20all%20the%20persons%20was%20done%20in%20the%20second%20phase.%20To%20ensure%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20data%2C%20we%20did%20random%20scrutiny%20of%20five%20percent%20of%20the%20data%20and%20prepared%20the%20final%20report.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20had%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20to%20stop%20the%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPublic%20interest%20litigations%20(PIL)%20were%20filed%20against%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20Patna%20high%20court%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20Justice%20Madhuresh%20Prasad%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%20PILs%2C%20had%20put%20an%20interim%20stay%20and%20fixed%20July%203%20for%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20on%20August%201%20had%20upheld%20the%20caste%20survey%20dismissing%20petitions%20filed%20against%20it.%C2%A0Petitioners%20then%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2021%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20told%20the%20petitioners%20that%20it%20would%20not%20stay%20the%20exercise%20unless%20they%20made%20out%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20petitioners%20had%20argued%20that%20legally%20the%20caste%20census%20can%20not%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20state%20government%20as%20only%20the%20central%20government%20has%20the%20right%20to%20do%20so%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20allowed%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20representing%20the%20Centre%2C%20to%20file%20its%20response%20on%20the%20issue%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20questioning%20the%20caste%20census.%20The%20affidavit%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20body%20under%20the%20Constitution%20or%20otherwise%20is%20entitled%20to%20conduct%20the%20exercise%20of%20either%20census%20or%20any%20action%20akin%20to%20census.%E2%80%9D%20But%20later%20it%20filed%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20withdrawing%20the%20paragraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20figures%20will%20set%20a%20benchmark%20for%20the%20country%20in%20giving%20representation%20to%20deprived%20and%20oppressed%20sections%20and%20the%20poor%20as%20per%20their%20population%20and%20to%20make%20policies%20for%20their%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20political%20fallout%20of%20census%20data%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20The%20government%20has%20released%20the%20data%20of%20a%20total%20of%20209%20castes%20in%20Bihar.%20Earlier%20the%20figures%20of%20these%20castes%20were%20estimated%20as%20the%20last%20caste%20census%20was%20done%20in%20the%201930s.%20But%2C%20now%20that%20their%20official%20numbers%20have%20come%20out%2C%20efforts%20will%20be%20made%20to%20create%20political%20vote%20banks%20according%20to%20the%20population%20of%20these%20castes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Naval%20Kishore%20Chaudhary%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20caste%20census%20has%20been%20conducted%20so%20that%20the%20castes%20can%20be%20consolidated.%20Now%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20figures%2C%20parties%20representing%20different%20castes%20will%20demand%20reservation.%20Caste%20enumeration%20is%20completely%20a%20political%20move.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20population%20of%20the%20OBC%20group%20and%20EBC%20group%20is%2063%25%2C%20which%20is%20most%20important%20from%20the%20election%20point%20of%20view.%20Yadavs%20also%20have%20the%20largest%20population%20among%20OBCs%2C%20about%2014.26%25.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Muslims%20is%20about%2017.70%25.%20Together%20the%20figure%20comes%20to%2031%25%20and%20both%20are%20considered%20core%20vote%20banks%20of%20RJD%2C%20so%20electorally%20RJD%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20a%20strong%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20votes%20of%20EBC%20castes%20are%20scattered%20among%20small%20political%20parties%2C%20so%20political%20parties%20will%20now%20try%20to%20mobilise%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Nai%20caste%20population%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20negligible%20but%20the%20census%20has%20revealed%20their%20population%20at%201.56%25.%20Similarly%2C%20Dusadh%2C%20Dhari%20and%20Dharahi%20castes%20had%20no%20estimated%20figure%20but%20current%20data%20revealed%20their%20population%20at%205.31%20percent%20whereas%20Chamar%20caste%20population%20stands%20at%205.25%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatna-based%20journalist%20Dipak%20Mishra%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20small%20castes%20had%20no%20bargaining%20power%20as%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20negligible%20in%20numbers.%20But%2C%20now%20they%20have%20data%20so%20they%20will%20bargain%20and%20political%20parties%20will%20also%20try%20to%20accommodate%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20RJD%20leader%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20%E2%80%9CBased%20on%20these%20data%2C%20we%20will%20make%20the%20next%20election%20strategies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20seen%20in%20terms%20of%20population%2C%20the%20latest%20figures%20remain%20around%20the%20earlier%20estimated%20figures.%20The%20figures%20that%20have%20been%20reported%20so%20far%20regarding%20the%20population%20of%20OBC%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Upper%20Caste%2C%20etc.%20are%20almost%20similar%20to%20the%20figures%20obtained%20in%20this%20calculation.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20political%20analysts%20do%20not%20see%20the%20possibility%20that%20these%20figures%20will%20yield%20any%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Mahendra%20Suman%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20figures%20that%20have%20just%20come%20confirm%20the%20earlier%20estimates.%20Yes%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20earlier%20we%20had%20estimated%20figures%20and%20now%20we%20have%20official%20figures.%20So%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20political%20significance%20of%20these%20figures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20questions%20will%20be%20raised%20about%20Yadav%20and%20Rajput%2C%20whose%20population%20is%2014.26%25%20and%203.45%25%2C%20because%20in%20the%202015%20and%202020%20assembly%20elections%2C%20these%20two%20castes%20and%20some%20other%20dominant%20castes%20were%20given%20much%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20population%20and%20they%20also%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRJD%20and%20JDU%20cannot%20take%20any%20benefit%20from%20these%20figures%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20population%20alone%2C%20rather%20questions%20will%20be%20raised%20on%20them%20that%20they%20do%20not%20give%20tickets%20as%20per%20population.%20Yes%2C%20if%20the%20report%20of%20socioeconomic%20conditions%20of%20these%20castes%20is%20released%2C%20it%20will%20benefit%20them%20because%20these%20data%20will%20tell%20what%20is%20the%20social%20status%20of%20the%20castes%20and%20accordingly%20reservation%20demand%20will%20be%20intensified%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Dipak%20Mishra%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20may%20help%20RJD%20and%20JDU%20to%20some%20extent%20but%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20of%20the%20Mandal%20era%20of%2090s%2C%20what%20RJD%20is%20expecting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYadav%20and%20Muslims%20were%20together%20about%2033%25%20but%20RJD%20had%20to%20lose%20in%202005%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696259119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16191410%2F2022_8img15_Aug_2022_PTI08_15_2022_000050B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-caste-census-released-at-63-obc-ebc-groups-set-to-take-pole-position-in-state-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Together%2C%20OBCs%2C%20EBCs%2C%20SCs%2C%20and%20STs%20account%20for%2084%25%20of%20the%20state%20population.%20At%2014.26%25%2C%20Yadavas%20are%20numerically%20preponderant%20group%20among%20OBCs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22