naire%20and%20mining%20tycoon%20Harpal%20Randhawa%20and%20his%2022-year-old%20son%20Amer%20were%20among%20six%20people%20who%20died%C2%A0in%20a%20plane%20crash%C2%A0in%20Zimbabwe%20on%20September%2029%2C%20as%20per%20a%20PTI%20report.%20The%20tragic%20incident%20occurred%20when%20their%20private%20plane%20crashed%20near%20a%20diamond%20mine%20in%20southwestern%20Zimbabwe%20after%20experiencing%20a%20technical%20fault%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0Harpal%20Randhawa%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20RioZim%2C%20a%20diversified%20mining%20company%20producing%20gold%20and%20coal%20as%20well%20as%20refining%20nickel%20and%20copper.%20Mr%20Randhawa%20also%20founded%20the%20%244-billion%20private%20equity%20business%20GEM%20Holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mining%20tycoon%20and%20his%20son%20were%20traveling%20in%20a%20Cessna%20206%20aircraft%2C%20privately%20owned%20by%20RioZim.%20They%20were%20en%20route%20from%20Harare%20to%20the%20Murowa%20diamond%20mine%20when%20the%20accident%20happened.%C2%A0The%20single-engined%20aircraft%20crashed%20near%20the%20Murowa%20Diamonds%20mine%2C%20which%20is%20partly%20owned%20by%20RioZim.%C2%A0All%20passengers%20and%20crew%20onboard%20died%20in%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFilmmaker%20Hopewell%20Chinono%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20Mr%20Randhawa%2C%20condoled%20his%20death%20on%20X%20and%20wrote%2C%20''I%20am%20deeply%20saddened%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20Harpal%20Randhawa%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Rio%20Zim%20who%20died%20in%20a%20plane%20crash%20in%20Zvishavane.%205%20other%20people%20including%20his%20son%20who%20was%20also%20a%20pilot%2C%20but%20a%20passenger%20on%20this%20flight%20also%20died%20in%20the%20crash.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20tweet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20am%20deeply%20saddened%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20Harpal%20Randhawa%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Rio%20Zim%20who%20died%20today%20in%20a%20plane%20crash%20in%20Zvishavane.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%205%20other%20people%20including%20his%20son%20who%20was%20also%20a%20pilot%2C%20but%20a%20passenger%20on%20this%20flight%20also%20died%20in%20the%20crash.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20I%20first%20met%20Harpal%20in%202017%20through%20a%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA0AGOaR3sw%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FA0AGOaR3sw%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Hopewell%20Chin'ono%20(%40daddyhope)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdaddyhope%2Fstatus%2F1707766776237305958%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E''He%20was%20very%20generous%20with%20life%20advice%2C%20and%20very%20humble%20for%20the%20wealthy%20man%20that%20he%20was.%20Through%20him%2C%20I%20met%20many%20people%20in%20the%20business%2C%20diplomatic%2C%20and%20political%20worlds.%20My%20thoughts%20are%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20the%20Rio%20Zim%20community.%20Rest%20in%20Peace%2C%20your%20works%20and%20love%20for%20Zimbabwe%20will%20be%20your%20lasting%20legacy%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Chinono%20also%20put%20up%20a%20tweet%20informing%20of%20the%20memorial%20service%20for%20the%20father-son%20duo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20family%20of%20Harpal%20Randhawa%20who%20died%20with%20his%20son%20Amer%20on%20Friday%20in%20a%20plane%20crash%2C%20respectfully%20invite%20all%20his%20friends%20and%20associates%20to%20celebrate%20his%20life%20and%20that%20of%20his%20son%20Amer%20at%20a%20memorial%20service%20at%20Raintree%20on%20Wednesday%20the%204th%20of%20October%2C%202023.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Arrival%20time%20is%203PM.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcWF0kPhe7G%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcWF0kPhe7G%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Hopewe