-power-rahul-4437729%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20thing%20we%20will%20do%20is%20to%20go%20for%20caste-based%20census%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20know%20exact%20number%20of%20OBCs...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20Bihar%20government%20report%20today%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20the%20Congress%20reiterates%20its%20demand%20that%20the%20union%20government%20conduct%20a%20national%20caste%20census%20at%20the%20earliest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20(Congress-led)%20UPA%20government%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20completed%20this%20census%20but%20its%20results%20were%20not%20published%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Such%20a%20census%20is%20essential%20for%20providing%20a%20firmer%20foundation%20for%20social%20empowerment%20programmes%20and%20for%20deepening%20social%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20party%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPressure%20on%20the%20BJP%20to%20conduct%20a%20national%20caste%20census%20will%20increase%20after%20today%2C%20following%20the%20Bihar%20government%20report%20that%20said%20around%2063%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20state's%20population%20hail%20from%20backward%20classes%2C%20and%20over%2020%20per%20cent%20are%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20or%20Tribes.%20The%20'general%20population'%20-%20which%20includes%20so-called%20upper%20classes%20that%20dominated%20Bihar%20politics%20till%20the%20Mandal%20report%20-%20is%20about%2015.5%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20-%20released%20months%20before%20a%20general%20election%20in%20a%20state%20that%20has%2040%20parliamentary%20seats%2C%2039%20of%20which%20were%20won%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20in%20the%202019%20election%20-%20will%20ramp%20up%20tension%20as%20states%20push%20for%20similar%20exercises%20and%20the%20opposition%20demands%20the%20centre%20hold%20a%20nation-wide%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt