20benefited%20by%20the%20tariffs%20it%20imposed%20on%20Washington%20that%20drove%20demand%20for%20imports%20towards%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20region%2C%20especially%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20IRA%20and%20new%20chip%20rules%20in%202022%20turned%20the%20tide%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20US.%20They%20have%20hit%20south-east%20Asian%20countries%20as%20their%20exports%20of%20affected%20products%20to%20the%20US%20have%20fallen.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696251180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F88qpnn68_china-economy-visa-_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-bank-downgrades-east-asias-growth-forecast-due-to-slowdown-in-china-report-4443109%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20World%20Bank%20cited%20tumbling%20retail%20sales%20tumbling%2C%20stagnant%20house%20prices%20and%20increased%20household%20debt%20for%20China's%20economic%20mess.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-bank-downgrades-east-asias-growth-forecast-due-to-slowdown-in-china-report-4443109%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-bank-downgrades-east-asias-growth-forecast-due-to-slowdown-in-china-report-4443109%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworld-bank-downgrades-east-asias-growth-forecast-due-to-slowdown-in-china-report-4443109%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Work%20starts%20on%20turning%20Adolf%20Hitler's%20birthplace%20into%20police%20station%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696251143000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104109854%2Cimgsize-1503622.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwork-starts-on-turning-adolf-hitlers-birthplace-in-austria-into-police-station%2Farticleshow%2F104109637.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104109637.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20in%20Austria%20where%20Adolf%20Hitler%20was%20born%20will%20be%20transformed%20into%20a%20police%20station%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20discourage%20Nazi%20sympathizers%20from%20visiting.%20The%20building%2C%20located%20in%20Braunau%20am%20Inn%2C%20will%20house%20the%20district%20police%20headquarters%20and%20a%20security%20academy%20branch.%20The%20decision%20to%20repurpose%20the%20building%20was%20made%20in%202019%20after%20a%20long%20dispute%20over%20its%20ownership.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwork-starts-on-turning-adolf-hitlers-birthplace-in-austria-into-police-station%2Farticleshow%2F104109637.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwork-starts-on-turning-adolf-hitlers-birthplace-in-austria-into-police-station%2Famp_articleshow%2F104109637.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwork-starts-on-turning-adolf-hitlers-birthplace-in-austria-into-police-station%2Famp_articleshow%2F104109637.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Copyright%20On%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20But...%3A%20Delhi%20High%20Court's%20Big%20Piracy%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20restrained%20several%20entities%20from%20reproducing%20and%20disseminating%20content%20belonging%20to%20the%20Bhaktivedanta%20Book%20Trust%2C%20established%20by%20ISKCON%20founder%20Srila%20Prabhupada%2C%20saying%20while%20there%20can%20be%20no%20copyright%20on%20religious%20scriptures%2C%20their%20adaptations%20which%20are%20%26quot%3Btransformative%20works%26quot%3B%20-%20like%20Ramanand%20Sagar's%20Ramayana%20or%20BR%20Chopra's%20Mahabharat%20-%20are%20entitled%20to%20protection%20from%20piracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Prathiba%20M%20Singh%2C%20hearing%20the%20Trust's%20lawsuit%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20said%20copyright%20would%20vest%20in%20original%20parts%20of%20works%20which%20preach%2C%20teach%2C%20or%20explain%20the%20scripture%20and%20the%20piracy%20of%20such%20copyrighted%20works%20of%20the%20plaintiff%20cannot%20be%20permitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefendant%20No%201%20to%2014%20shall%20stand%20restrained%20in%20any%20manner%20from%20printing%2C%20reproducing%2C%20communicating%2C%20disseminating%20any%20part%20of%20the%20Plaintiff's%20works%20to%20the%20public%20either%20in%20print%20form%20or%20in%20audio-visual%20form%20or%20in%20electronic%20form%20including%20through%20websites%2C%20mobile%20applications%2C%20weblinks%2C%20Instagram%20posts%20or%20any%20other%20posts%20on%20the%20social%20media%20as%20would%20result%20in%20the%20infringement%20of%20the%20plaintiff's%20copyright%2C%26quot%3B%20ordered%20the%20court%20recently%20in%20an%20ex-parte%20interim%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20directed%20Google%20and%20Meta%20to%20take%20down%20the%20infringing%20works%20from%20their%20platforms%20while%20ordering%20the%20suspension%20and%20blocking%20of%20the%20offending%20links%20by%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiff%20submitted%20that%20it%20has%20copyright%20on%20all%20works%20of%20spiritual%20teacher%20Abhay%20Charanaravinda%20Bhaktivedanta%20Swami%20Prabhupada%20who%20simplified%20the%20religious%20books%20and%20scriptures%20and%20made%20it%20easy%20for%20the%20common%20man%20to%20understand%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20stated%20that%20during%20Prabhupada's%20lifetime%20and%20after%20his%20%26quot%3BMahasamadhi%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20plaintiff%20spread%20his%20teachings%20in%20various%20forms%2C%20including%20printed%20and%20audiobooks%2C%20and%20the%20defendants%20were%20making%20them%20available%20on%20their%20online%20platforms%2C%20mobile%20apps%2C%20and%20Instagram%20handles%20without%20any%20licence%20or%20the%20right%20to%20reproduce%20or%20communicate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20Shrimad%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20revered%20ancient%20scriptures%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20along%20with%20the%20other%20scriptures%20like%20Bhagavatam%20which%20are%20written%20about%20by%20the%20author%20(Prabhupada)%20are%20all%20public%20domain%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20copyright%20claimed%20in%20the%20scriptures.%20However%2C%20any%20adaptations%20of%20the%20said%20work%20including%20providing%20an%20explanation%2C%20summary%2C%20meaning%2C%20exegesis%2Finterpretation%20or%20creating%20any%20audio-visual%20works%20for%20example%20television%20series%20like%20Ramanand%20Sagar's%20Ramayana%20or%20BR%20Chopra's%20Mahabharata%2C%20dramatic%20works%20created%20by%20drama%20societies%20based%20on%20scriptures%20etc%2C%20being%20transformative%20works%2C%20would%20be%20entitled%20to%20copyright%20protection%20-%20being%20original%20works%20of%20the%20authors%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20though%20there%20can%20be%20no%20objection%20in%20the%20actual%20reproduction%20of%20the%20text%20of%20Shrimad%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20or%20other%20spiritual%20books%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20they%20are%20interpreted%20by%20different%20gurus%20and%20spiritual%20teachers%20%26quot%3Bcopyright%20would%20vest%20in%20respect%20of%20the%20original%20parts%20of%20the%20literary%20works%20which%20preach%2C%20teach%20or%20explain%20the%20scripture.%26quot%3B%20The%20court%20stated%20that%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20Prabhupada%20himself%20set%20up%20the%20plaintiff%20Trust%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20copyrights%20to%20be%20administered%20by%20the%20trust%20and%20the%20defendant's%20content%20was%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20reproduction%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20cannot%20be%20done%20without%20authorisation%2C%20licence%2C%20or%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20not%20mere%20reproductions%20of%20the%20original%20scriptures%20but%20their%20meaning%2C%20summary%2C%20introduction%2C%20preface%2C%20cover%2C%20etc.%2C%20have%20all%20been%20reproduced%2C%20the%20court%20observed%2C%20adding%20that%20such%20conduct%20has%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20plaintiff's%20revenue%20from%20the%20copyrighted%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20piracy%20of%20the%20copyrighted%20works%20of%20the%20Plaintiff-Trust%20cannot%20be%20permitted.%20If%20such%20piracy%20goes%20unchecked%2C%20the%20copyright%20on%20the%20said%20works%20would%20be%20considerably%20diluted%20leading%20to%20immense%20loss%20of%20revenues%20to%20the%20Plaintiff-Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20these%20circumstances%2C%20this%20court%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20plaintiff%20has%20made%20out%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20for%20grant%20of%20an%20ex-parte%20ad%20interim%20injunction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696251060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Ft72t3c1g_delhi-high-court-650_625x300_11_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-copyright-on-scriptures-but-delhi-high-court-big-piracy-ruling-4442784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20restrained%20several%20entities%20from%20reproducing%20and%20disseminating%20content%20of%20the%20Bhaktivedanta%20Book%20Trust%2C%20saying%20while%20there%20can%20be%20no%20copyright%20on%20religious%20scriptures%2C%20their%20adaptations%20are%20entitled%20to%20protection%20from%20piracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalU