tution%20that%20does%20not%20trust%20its%20legislators%20has%20to%20lay%20down%20an%20excruciating%20detail%20of%20what%20rules%20of%20procedure%20they%20must%20adopt%E2%80%9D.%20Once%20again%2C%20look%20at%20the%20record%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20point%20out%20again%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20only%20using%20it%20as%20an%20example.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20run%20rough%20shots%20over%20procedures%20right%20through%20nine%20years%2C%20which%20is%20why%20when%20the%20constitution%20lays%20down%20in%20what%20you%20call%20%E2%80%9Cexcruciating%20detail%E2%80%9D%2C%20how%20they%20must%20be%20followed.%20The%20constitution%20is%20hoping%20to%20tell%20people%20as%20powerful%20as%20Modi%2C%20%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20there%20are%20ways%20of%20doing%20things%2C%20the%20means%20are%20as%20important%20as%20the%20end%2C%20the%20right%20means%20are%20necessary%E2%80%9D.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20if%20you%20lay%20it%20down%20in%20that%20way%2C%20that%20a%20man%20with%20the%20power%20of%20Modi%20is%20hopefully%20encouraged%20to%20fulfil%20the%20procedure.%20Even%20then%20he%20violates%20it%2C%20but%20at%20least%20the%20constitution%20making%20an%20effort%20to%20tell%20procedure%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArghya%20Sengupta%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20I%20just%20feel%20that%20this%20cannot%20happen%20by%20dictation.%20This%20is%20something%20that%20is%20a%20culture%20of%20compliance%20with%20law%2C%20which%20cannot%20happen%20because%20the%20constitution%20is%20saying%20in%20some%20painful%20detail%20as%20to%20how%20a%20bill%20is%20to%20be%20introduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKaran%20Thapar%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20But%20then%20the%20corollary%20to%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20is%20that%20the%20culture%20of%20compliance%20with%20law%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20exist%20in%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArghya%20Sengupta%3C%2Fb%3E%3A%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20much%20larger%20case%2C%20because%20I%20think%20that%20we%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20fall%20into%20the%20tr