ople%2C%20needlessly%20good%20and%20kind%20and%20generous%20to%20them%2C%20whereas%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been.%20But%20let%20me%20end%20with%20what%20I%20think%20is%20very%20interesting%2C%20and%20this%20is%20literally%20my%20last%20question.%20Despite%20your%20criticism%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20you%20are%20not%20calling%20for%20a%20new%20constitution.%20You%20write%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20a%20call%20to%20draft%20a%20new%20constitution%20today.%20We%20live%20in%20polarised%20times%2C%20and%20any%20constitution%20that%20emerges%20after%20such%20a%20time%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20long%20lasting%E2%80%9D.%20So%20you%20would%20fundamentally%20disagree%20with%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%2C%20Bibek%20Debroy%2C%20who%20recently%20wrote%20an%20article%20in%20%3Ci%3EMint%3C%2Fi%3E%20calling%20for%20a%20new%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FlaWeb3Qqq_k%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22We%20Have%20Veiled%20Emergency%2C%20Judges%20Often%20Lack%20Spine%2C%20Writing%20New%20Constitution%20at%20This%20Time%20Impossible%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArghya%20Sengupta%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EIf%20the%20question%20is%20one%20of%20timing%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20this%20is%20a%20time%20to%20write%20a%20new%20constitution.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20at%20all%2C%20because%20if%20we%20have%20some%20ideas%20that%20we%20think%20will%20serve%20India%20better%20then%20we%20need%20consensus%20on%20those%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKaran%20Thapar%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20missing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArghya%20Sengupta%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EConsensus%20is%20completely%20missing%20from%20the%20political%20spectrum%20today%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20number%20one.%20But%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20we%20have%2