0in%20which%20we%20expand%20the%20freedoms%20and%20rights%20that%20we%20have%2C%20and%20we%20always%20need%20to%20discuss%20how%20we%20ensure%20that%20those%20who%20are%20charged%20with%20defending%20them%20and%20implementing%20them%20become%20better%20at%20it%2C%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20actually%20abuse%20them%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens.%20I%20agree%20with%20you%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArghya%20Sengupta%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EExactly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKaran%20Thapar%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThank%20you%20very%20much%20indeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArghya%20Sengupta%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThank%20you%2C%20Karan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696240823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F02141920%2FScreenshot-2023-10-02-at-2.18.13.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffull-text-transcript-karan-thapar-arghya-sengupta-colonial-constitution%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Is%20India's%20constitution%20colonial%3F%20Or%20is%20it%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20opposite%3F%20Karan%20Thapar%20questions%20Arghya%20Sengupta's%20views%20on%20the%20matter%20in%20this%20lively%20interview.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffull-text-transcript-karan-thapar-arghya-sengupta-colonial-constitution%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parineeti-Raghav's%20fun%20pre-wedding%20video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696240681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104106062%2Cimgsize-56630.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fchopra-vs-chadha-parineeti-raghav-paint-the-internet-red-with-yet-another-fun-pre-wedding-video-watch%2Farticleshow%2F104106016.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%2