ng%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Prasar%20Bharati%20said%20on%20October%201%20(Sunday)%20that%20it%20does%20not%20make%20copyright%20claims%20on%20public%20service%20content%2C%20including%20parliamentary%20proceedings.%20This%20statement%20came%20in%20response%20to%20allegations%20that%20it%20had%20sent%20copyright%20infringement%20notices%20to%20YouTubers%20regarding%20parliamentary%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGurdeep%20Singh%20Sappal%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20executive%20officer%2Feditor%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20TV%2C%20raised%20the%20issue%20and%20argued%20that%20parliamentary%20proceedings%20are%20national%20assets%20of%20historical%20value%20and%20should%20be%20freely%20accessible%2C%20not%20subject%20to%20copyright.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrasar%20Bharti%20has%20sent%20notices%20to%20YouTubers%20invoking%20copyright%20on%20it.%20This%20is%20wrong.%20Parliamentary%20proceedings%20are%20national%20assets%20of%20historical%20value.%20They%20are%20not%20a%20commercial%20product%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20profiteering%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20copyright.%20In%20fact%2C%20any%20attempt%20to%20limit%20the%20access%20to%20parliamentary%20proceedings%20amounts%20to%20censorship%20and%20is%20an%20infringement%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20citizens%20(to)%20be%20informed%20of%20the%20happenings%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sappal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20part%20of%20parliamentary%20debate%20can%20only%20be%20restricted%20from%20public%20access%20by%20a%20specific%20order%20of%20the%20Chair%20only%2C%20using%20the%20powers%20vested%20in%20them%20to%20expunge%20parts%20of%20proceedings.%20When%20I%20had%20started%20RSTV%2C%20this%20issue%20was%20deliberated%20upon%20by%20the%20Content%20Advisory%20Committee%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20It%20was%20the%20unanimous%20decision%20that%20parliamentary%20proceedings%20have%20to%20be%20provided%20to%20anyone%20free%20of%20cost%2C%20to%20be%20used%20freely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Prasar%20Bharati%20officials%20emphasised%20that%20they%20had%20never%20issued%20such%20copyright%20notices%2C%20and%20their%20public%20service-related%20content%20is%20copyright-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fprasar-bharati-does-not-make-copyright-claims-on-public-service-content-say-officials%2Farticle67369734.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20sometimes%20copyright%20violation%20notices%20might%20be%20automatically%20generated%20due%20to%20platform%20algorithms%2C%20but%20they%20encourage%20affected%20individuals%20to%20contest%20such%20notices%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20promptly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20this%20matter%20has%20not%20been%20released%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20report%2C%20Sappal%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20statement%20attributed%20to%20Prasar%20Bharti%20officials%20would%20have%20been%20a%20welcome%20one%2C%20if%20only%20it%20were%20an%20official%20statement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20intent%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti%20is%20indeed%20not%20to%20claim%20copyright%20over%20the%20usage%20of%20Parliamentary%20proceedings%2C%20then%20it%20must%20issue%20an%20official%20statement%20clarifying%20it.%20Such%20a%20statement%20can%20then%20be%20used%20by%20social%20media%20content%20creators%20for%20their%20official%20reply%20to%20the%20notices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20statement%20attributed%20to%20Prasar%20Bharti%20officials%20would%20have%20been%20a%20welcome%20one%2C%20if%20only%20it%20were%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20intent%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti%20is%20indeed%20not%20to%20claim%20copyright%20over%20the%20usage%20of%20Parliamentary%20proceedings%2C%20then%20it%