ky.com%2Fstory%2Fuk-hands-4bn-contract-to-bae-systems-for-powerful-attack-submarines-as-part-of-aukus-pact-12974882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fuk-hands-4bn-contract-to-bae-systems-for-powerful-attack-submarines-as-part-of-aukus-pact-12974882%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fuk-hands-4bn-contract-to-bae-systems-for-powerful-attack-submarines-as-part-of-aukus-pact-12974882%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thousands%20Protest%20in%20Delhi%20Demanding%20Restoration%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F02141625%2FF7WJ7MBbgAAs4cz.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thousands%20of%20government%20employees%20gathered%20at%20the%20Ram%20Lila%20Maidan%20of%20the%20national%20capital%20to%20protest%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20National%20Pension%20Scheme%20and%20demand%20full%20restoration%20of%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20on%20Sunday%20(October%201).%20The%20protestors%20comprised%20Central%20and%20state%20government%20employees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20those%20of%20the%20public%20sector%20units%20of%20over%2020%20states.%20Termed%20the%20%E2%80%9CPension%20Shanknaad%20Rally%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20protest%20was%20organised%20by%20the%20National%20Movement%20for%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20(NMOPS)%2C%20as%20association%20steering%20the%20campaign%20for%20restoration%20of%20the%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20PTI%2C%20NMOPS%20leader%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Bandhu%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20spreading%20the%20message%20for%20OPS%20restoration%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20old%20pension%20has%20been%20restored%20in%20four%20or%20five%20states%20through%20our%20efforts%20and%20struggle.%20Our%20team%20believes%20that%20if%20the%20central%20government%20ratifies%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%2C%20then%20the%20onus%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20on%20the%20state%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20employees%20who%20joined%20government%20service%20after%20January%201%2C%202004%2C%20are%20strongly%20opposing%20the%20New%20Pension%20Scheme.%20The%20employees%20are%20worried%20about%20their%20future%20after%20retirement%20because%20they%20are%20being%20forced%20into%20the%20NPS%20and%20deprived%20of%20the%20OPS%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shiv%20Gopal%20Mishra%2C%20national%20convener%20and%20general%20secretary%20of%20All%20India%20Railway%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Federation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmanorama.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2023%2F10%2F01%2Fmassive-protest-rally-delhi-govt-employees-against-new-pension-scheme.html%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EManorama%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20NPS%20was%20introduced%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20government%20employees%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20it.%20While%20OPS%20factored%20in%20inflation%20and%20pension%20payouts%20based%20on%20pay%20commission%20indices%20without%20any%20contribution%20from%20the%20employee%2C%20the%20NPS%20is%20decided%20by%20the%20contribution%20of%20both%20the%20employee%20and%20the%20employer%20and%20the%20returns%20are%20market-based%20instead%20of%20a%20fixed%20sum%20based%20on%20the%20salary%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fopposition-ex-military-personnel-new-disability-pension-rules-slam%5C%22%3EOpposition%2C%20Ex-Military%20Personnel%20Slam%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20New%20Disability%20Pension%20Rules%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20argued%20that%20the%20NPS%20will%20put%20much%20lesser%20burden%20on%20the%20government%20exchequer%20than%20the%20OPS%2C%20and%20the%20probability%20of%20higher%20returns%20is%20high.%20However%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20government%20employees%20opposed%20the%20linking%20of%20pensions%20with%20the%20market%20and%20saw%20the%20move%20as%20a%20further%20depletion%20in%20employee%E2%80%99s%20social%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20has%20become%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20and%20opposition%20forces.%20Many%20opposition-ruled%20states%20like%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Punjab%20have%20already%20scrapped%20the%20NPS%20in%20favour%20of%20OPS.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20was%20largely%20credited%20to%20the%20grand-old%20party%E2%80%99s%20poll%20promise%20of%20implementing%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20several%20opposition%20leaders%20joined%20the%20protest%20to%20support%20government%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20declared%20his%20support%20for%20OPS%20at%20the%20site.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20fully%20supported%20the%20legitimate%20demand%20of%20the%20employee%20organisations%20associated%20with%20NMOPS.%20As%20soon%20as%20the%20Congress%20government%20is%20formed%20in%20Haryana%2C%20we%20will%20immediately%20fulfill%20this%20demand%20of%20the%20employees%20for%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20who%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20event%20were%20Congress%20leaders%20Arvinder%20Singh%20Lovely%2C%20Sandeep%20Dixit%20and%20Udit%20Raj%2C%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20leader%20Shyam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20and%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leader%20Rakesh%20Tikait.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupporting%20the%20OPS%2C%20the%20Congress%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%E2%80%9COld%20pension%20is%20the%20right%20of%20the%20employees.%20Congress%20state%20governments%20have%20restored%20the%20old%20pension.%20Our%20policy%20regarding%20this%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20employees%20must%20get%20their%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3