C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20an%20edited%20excerpt%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EReading%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20Twenty-First%20Century%2C%3Cem%3E%C2%A0by%20%3C%2Fem%3ENiranjan%20Ramakrishnan%3Cem%3E%20(Palgrave%20Pivot%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EPalgrave%20Macmillan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%202013).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20theory%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20wag%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthings%20should%20be%20the%20same%20in%20theory%20and%20practice.%20In%20practice%2C%20though%2C%20they%20aren%E2%80%99t.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20serve%20to%20explain%20why%20every%20modern%20state%20has%20only%20grown%20powerful%20over%20time%2C%20instead%20of%20becoming%20irrelevant%20as%20theory%20ordains.%20%5BEven%5D%20when%20it%20has%20gone%20from%20one%20ideology%20to%20its%20diametrical%20opposite%2C%20the%20state%20itself%20has%20never%20looked%20discomfited%20in%20the%20slightest%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20consistent%20abuse%2C%20the%20state%2C%20always%20a%20little%20suspect%20for%20its%20motives%2C%20is%20firmly%20established%20in%20the%20public%20mind%20as%20just%20another%20arm%20of%20a%20particular%20dispensation%2C%20not%20an%20impartial%20and%20benign%20entity%20sitting%20above%20the%20fray.%20The%20Hindi%20adage%20%3Cem%3Ejiski%20lathi%20uski%20bhains%20%3C%2Fem%3E(he%20who%20holds%20the%20stick%20gets%20the%20buffalo)%2C%20conveys%20exactly%20this%20truth.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20wielders%20of%20state%20power%2C%20too%2C%20in%20such%20a%20context%2C%20come%20to%20view%20it%20as%20a%20routine%20accessory%20to%20their%20plans%20and%20purposes.%20That%20such%20corruption%20can%20seize%20alike%20a%20capitalist%2C%20communist%2C%20or%20any%20other%20type%20of%20state%20is%20hardly%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%20instinctively%20grasped%20the%20underlying%20purpose%20of%20the%20state%2C%20and%20therefore%20its%20nature%3B%20squabbles%20over%20its%20intent%20to%20reconcile%20or%20suppress%20class%20divisions%20were%20just%20a%20sideshow%20to%20a%20more%20serious%20aspect.%20The%20state%20was%20the%20antithesis%20of%20the%20individual%2C%20and%20of%20ahimsa%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20state%20represents%20violence%20in%20a%20concentrated%20and%20organized%20form.%20The%20individual%20has%20a%20soul%2C%20but%20as%20the%20State%20is%20a%20soulless%20machine%2C%20it%20can%20never%20be%20weaned%20from%20violence%20to%20which%20it%20owes%20its%20very%20existence%E2%80%A6.I%20look%20upon%20an%20increase%20of%20the%20power%20of%20the%20state%20with%20the%20greatest%20fear%2C%20because%20all%20the%20while%20apparently%20doing%20good%20by%20minimizing%20exploitation%2C%20it%20does%20the%20greatest%20harm%20to%20mankind%20by%20destroying%20individuality%2C%20which%20lies%20at%20the%20root%20of%20all%20progress.%E2%80%9D%20%5BGandhi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CInterview%20with%20N.K%20Bose%2C%201934%3B%20reproduced%20in%20%3C%2Fem%3ECollected%20Works%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20(CWMG)%2C%20VOL%2C%2065%2C%C2%A0%20p%20318%2C%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENearly%20three%20decades%20after%20these%20words%2C%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20general%20sense%20of%20unease%20with%20rampant%20state%20power%20was%20given%20more%20specific%20voice%20in%20an%20unlikely%20quarter%2C%20by%20no%20less%20than%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20industrialised%20world.%20Eisenhower%E2%80%99s%20words%20of%20caution%20could%20have%20come%20right%20out%20of%20one%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20journals%3B%20instead%2C%20they%20were%20the%20reflections%20of%20a%20general-statesman%20as%20he%20prepared%20to%20retire%20after%20two%20terms%20as%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%5B%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%20%3Cem%3Econjunction%20of%20an%20immense%20military%20establishment%20and%20a%20large%20arms%20industry%20is%20new%20in%20the%20American%20experience.%20The%20total%20influence%20%E2%80%93%20economic%2C%20political%2C%20even%20spiritual%20%E2%80%93%20is%20felt%20in%20every%20city%2C%20every%20State%20house%2C%20every%20office%20of%20the%20federal%20government.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20councils%20of%20government%2C%20we%20must%20guard%20against%20the%20acquisition%20of%20unwarranted%20influence%2C%20whether%20sought%20or%20unsought%2C%20by%20the%20military%20industrial%20complex.%20The%20potential%20for%20the%20disastrous%20rise%20of%20misplaced%20power%20exists%20and%20will%20persist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%5BEisenhower%E2%80%99s%20farewell%20address%2C%201961.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEisenhower%E2%80%99s%20warnings%20went%20unheeded%20in%20his%20own%20country.%20In%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20military-industrial%20mindset%20has%20taken%20firm%20roots%2C%20not%20least%20in%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20own%20native%20land%E2%80%A6%20In%20the%20five%20decades%20since%20Eisenhower%20gave%20his%20farewell%20address%2C%20spending%20on%20weapons%20worldwide%20has%20risen%20multi-fold.%20The%20military-industrial%20complex%20thrives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Where%20Is%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20India%20of%20Today%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fwhere-is-gandhi-in-the-india-of-today%5C%22%3EWhere%20Is%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20India%20of%20Today%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20not%20surprise%20Gandhi.%20The%20modern%20industrial%20state%20to%20him%20always%20appeared%20a%20tad%20specious.%20While%20his%20contemporaries%20were%20bowled%20over%20by%20its%20apparent%20benevolence%20and%20capacity%20for%20endless%20fulfillment%20of%20wants%2C%20he%20saw%20even%20in%20its%20best%20face%20a%20progressive%20entrapment%20of%20humanity%20with%20promises%20of%20comfort%20and%20consequence-(and%20conscience-)free%20enjoyment.%20He%20saw%2C%20too%2C%20that%20modern%20industry%20could%20not%20be%20sustained%20without%20centralization%20of%20power%20and%20a%20commensurate%20strengthening%20of%20the%20state.%20Far%20from%20being%20cause%20for%20celebration%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20a%20technocracy%20to%20mediate%20between%20people%20and%20the%20(industrial)%20plant%20often%20meant%20citizens%20ceding%20sovereignty%20for%20creature%20comforts.%20To%20him%20this%20was%20not%20a%20step%20towards%20human%20liberation%2C%20the%20instinctive%20measure%20by%20which%20he%20reckoned%20good%20or%20bad%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20suggest%20that%2C%20if%20India%20is%20to%20evolve%20along%20nonviolent%20lines%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20decentralize%20many%20things.%20Centralisation%20cannot%20be%20sustained%20and%20defended%20without%20adequate%20force%E2%80%A6%5B%3C%2Fem%3EHarijan%2C%20December%2030%2C%201939%2C%20CWMG%2C%20Vol%2077%2C%20p%20165%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20endless%20quest%20for%20resources%20on%20one%20side%20and%20markets%20on%20the%20other%20that%20industrialisation%20demanded%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20military%20logic%20required%20to%20secure%20the%20one%20or%20ensure%20the%20other%2C%20was%20to%20Gandhi%20the%20road%20to%20moral%2C%20if%20not%20material%2C%20bankruptcy%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20incessant%20search%20for%20material%20comforts%20and%20their%20multiplication%20is%20such%20an%20evil%2C%20and%20I%20make%20bold%20to%20say%20that%20the%C2%A0%20Europeans%20themselves%20will%20have%20to%20remodel%20their%20outlook%2C%20if%20they%20are%20not%20to%20perish%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20comforts%20to%20which%20they%20are%20becoming%20slaves.%20It%20may%20be%20that%20my%20reading%20is%20wrong%2C%20but%20I%20know%20that%20for%20India%20to%20run%20after%20the%20Golden%20Fleece%20is%20to%20court%20certain%20death.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BYoung%20India%2C%20%3Cem%3EApril%2030%2C%201931%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3ECWMG%2C%20Vol.%2052%2C%20p.%209%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20wages%20of%20pursuing%20the%20%E2%80%98Golden%20Fleece%E2%80%99%20were%20seldom%20better%20captured%20than%20in%20a%20piece%20by%20the%20soldier-scholae%20Andrew%20Bacevich%20pondering%20the%20shoals%20upon%20which%20a%2063-year%20spree%20of%20consumerism%20had%20marooned%20his%20country%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAmerican%20preoccupation%20with%20%E2%80%9Cmore%E2%80%9D%20has%20affected%20US%20relations%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20Yet%20the%20foreign%20policy%20implications%20of%20our%20self-indulgence%20are%20almost%20entirely%20negative.%20Over%20the%20past%20six%20decades%2C%20efforts%20to%20satisfy%20spiralling%20consumer%20demand%20have%20given%20birth%20to%20a%20condition%20of%20profound%20dependency.%20The%20ethic%20of%20self-gratification%20saddles%20us%20with%20costly%20commitments%20abroad%20that%20we%20are%20increasingly%20ill-equipped%20to%20sustain%20while%20confronting%20us%20with%20dangers%20to%20which%20we%20have%20no%20ready%20response.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B%3Cem%3EAndrew%20Basevich%2C%20%E2%80%98Appetite%20for%20Destruction%2C%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20American%20Conservative%2C%20September%208%2C%202008.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20writings%2C%20Basevich%20has%20pointed%20to%20the%20military-industrial%20state%2C%20despairing%20of%20the%20evident%20American%20democracy%20to%20rein%20in%20this%20Frankenstein%E2%80%99s%20monster%20in%20either%20of%20its%20incarnations%3A%20warmonger%20abroad%20or%20super-secret%20national%20security%20behemoth%20at%20home.%20But%20Gandhi%20had%20anticipated%20both%20Eisenhower%20and%20Basevich%2C%20getting%20right%20to%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20matter%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScience%20of%20war%20leads%20one%20to%20dictatorship%20pure%20and%20simple.%20Science%20of%20non-violence%20can%20alone%20lead%20one%20to%20pure%20democracy.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BHarijan%2C%20%3Cem%3EOctober%2015%2C%201938%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ECWMG%2C%20Vol%2074%2C%20p.%2089%C2%A0%20%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20speech%20referred%20to%20earlier%2C%20Eisenhower%20hoped%20that%20the%20American%20public%20would%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20burgeoning%20military-industrial%20complex%20so%20as%20to%20keep%20it%20from%20overrunning%20their%20very%20liberties%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20must%20never%20let%20the%20weight%20of%20this%20combination%20endanger%20our%20liberties%20or%20democratic%20processes%E2%80%A6.%20Only%20an%20alert%20and%20knowledgeable%20citizenry%20can%20compel%20the%20proper%20meshing%20of%20the%20huge%20industrial%20and%20military%20machinery%20of%20defense%20with%20our%20peaceful%20methods%20and%20goals%2C%20so%20that%20security%20and%20liberty%20may%20prosper%20together.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BEisenhower%E2%80%99s%20farewell%20address%2C%201961.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Is%20Gandhi%20Pass%C3%A9%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fis-gandhi-passe%5C%22%3EIs%20Gandhi%20Pass%C3%A9%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20fiftieth%20anniversary%20of%20Eisenhower%E2%80%99s%20address%2C%20many%20commentators%20pointed%20to%20his%20prescience%20and%20the%20unfolding%20of%20the%20very%20prospect%20he%20had%20feared%2C%20some%20even%20taking%20note%20of%20the%20remarkable%20lassitude%20with%20which%20Americans%20have%20tolerated%20it%20all.%20They%20would%20not%20have%20known%20that%20Gandhi%20had%20gone%20a%20step%20further%3A%20keeping%20the%20state%20in%20line%20would%20require%20not%20just%20an%20%E2%80%9Calert%20and%20knowledgeable%E2%80%9D%20citizenry%20but%20one%20actually%20prepared%20to%20offer%20civil%20disobedience%2C%20always%20keeping%20it%20in%20reserve%20as%20a%20permanent%20weapon%20of%20good%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECivil%20disobedience%2C%20therefore%2C%20becomes%20a%20sacred%20duty%20when%20the%20State%20has%20become%20lawless%2C%20or%20which%20is%20the%20same%20thing%2C%20corrupt.%20And%20a%20citizen%20that%20barters%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ewith%20such%20a%20State%20shares%20its%20corruption%20or%20lawlessness.%20It%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20possible%20to%20question%20the%20wisdom%20of%20applying%20civil%20disobedience%20in%20respect%20of%20a%20particular%20act%20or%20law%E2%80%A6.But%20the%20right%20itself%20cannot%20be%20surrendered%20without%20surrender%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20self-respect.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BYoung%20India%2C%20%3Cem%3EJanuary%205%2C%201922%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3ECWMG%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20As%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20civil%20disobedience%20is%20the%20only%20%E2%80%93%20and%20ultimate%20%E2%80%93%20safeguard%20against%20a%20state%20gone%20rogue%3A%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20a%20birthright%20that%20cannot%20be%20surrendered%20without%20surrender%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20self-respect.%E2%80%9D%20%5B%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98The%20Immediate%20Issue%E2%80%99%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EYoung%20India%2C%20%3Cem%3EJanuary%205%2C%201922%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ECWMG%2C%20%3Cem%3EVol%2025%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20p.%20392%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAy%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20the%20rub%2C%20as%20the%20old%20line%20goes.%20For%20only%20citizens%20can%20have%20self-respect%3B%20consumers%20merely%20understand%20value-for-money.%20In%20a%20silent%20(no%20pun%20intended)%20metamorphosis%2C%20the%20citizenry%20of%20Eisenhower%E2%80%99s%20time%20has%2C%20over%20the%20decades%2C%20become%20the%20consumer%20society%20of%20our%20own.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20glimpse%20into%20exactly%20what%20Gandhi%20feared%20a%20mindless%20march%20to%20industrialism%20would%20bring%20about%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fniranjan-ramakrishnan%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENiranjan%20Ramakrishnan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0was%20a%20long-time%20contributor%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECounterpunch%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eand%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECountercurrents%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eand%20his%20work%20has%20been%20carried%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Z-Mag%2C%20Common%20Dreams%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eand%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EDissident%20Voice.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAmong%20the%20print%20outlets%20that%20have%20featured%20his%20writings%20are%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0The%20Oregonian%2C%20the%20Indian%20Express%2C%20The%20Hindu%2C%20India%20Today%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0the%20Economic%20Times.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHis%20first%20book%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EBantaism%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20The%20Philosophy%20of%20Sardar%20Jokes%20(2011)%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ewas%20hailed%20for%20its%20audacity%20by%20noted%20author%20and%20historian%20Khushwant%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696210250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F01171000%2FMahatma_Gandhi_Bestanddeelnr_916-6994.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fi-look-upon-an-increase-of-the-power-of-the-state-with-the-greatest-fear%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gandhi%20warned%20us%20long%20ago%20that%20when%20citizens%20are%20turned%20into%20consumers%20by%20a%20modern%20industrial%20state%20intent%20on%20centralising%20power%2C%20erosion%20of%20democratic%20liberties%20follows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fi-look-upon-an-increase-of-the-power-of-the-state-with-the-greatest-fear%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20set%20to%20make%20surprise%20appearance%20at%20trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696209780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F70x70%2Fskynews-donald-trump-fraud_6305675.jpg%3F20231002024745%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdonald-trumps-fraud-trial-is-about-to-start-but-he-argues-his-rivals-are-out-to-get-him-12974758%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20is%20set%20to%20make%20a%20surprise%20appearance%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20his%20trial%20for%20%26quot%3Bastounding%26quot%3B%20fraud%20which%20begins%20in%20New%20York%20today.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A218%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdonald-trumps-fraud-trial-is-about-to-start-but-he-argues-his-rivals-are-out-to-get-him-12974758%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.co