ading%5C%22%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20give%20Hatmulla%20a%20%3Cem%3Echinar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplantation%20area%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ERealising%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20converted%2020%20hectares%20of%20barren%20land%20in%20Hatmulla%20into%20a%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20plantation%20unit%2C%20which%20currently%20has%20over%20300%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20trees.%20The%20unit%20has%20become%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20where%20the%20trees%20are%20cultivated%20on%20a%20mass%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20when%20we%20saw%20what%20Abdul%20Ahad%20Khan%20was%20doing%20with%20this%20barren%20land%2C%20we%20immediately%20converted%20the%2020-hectare%20plot%20into%20a%20reserve.%20We%20demarcated%20the%20area%20and%20erected%20fences%20to%20protect%20these%20%3Cem%3Echinar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants.%20Today%2C%20we%20have%20300%20such%20trees%20in%20this%20unit%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Zahid%20Mughal%2C%20district%20forest%20officer%20of%20Kamraj%2C%20Kupwara.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20forest%20department%20is%20using%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20proficiency%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F131803%2Frifat-abdullah-kashmir-environment-tree-plantation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacross%20all%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20plantation%20drives%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20district.%20%E2%80%9CKhan%20has%20a%20good%20knowledge%20about%20the%20cutting%20and%20planting%20of%20saplings%20with%20a%20minimal%20failure%20rate.%20Since%20he%20is%20a%20daily%20wage%20labourer%2C%20the%20department%20gives%20him%20work%20during%20the%20plantation%20season%20and%20while%20maintaining%20the%20trees%20in%20the%20district%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mughal%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201075px)%20100vw%2C%201075px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F