20history%3F%20We%20wanted%20to%20couple%20that%20idea%20with%20how%20people%20often%20overlook%20or%20forget%20waste%20as%20well%20and%20that%20is%20how%20we%20came%20up%20with%20a%20whole%20storyline%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20The%20technique%20employed%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20their%20Eve%20collection%20takes%20inspiration%20from%20the%20concept%20of%20Kintsugi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20to%20apply%20the%20same%20concept%20with%20scraps%20and%20join%20them%20with%20golden%20embroidery%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20zero%20wastage.%20We%20have%20created%20a%20whole%20fabric%20from%20waste%20threads%20coming%20out%20of%20shirts%20and%20T-shirts.%20As%20soon%20as%20you%20look%20at%20our%20collection%2C%20you%20can%20already%20see%20that%20there%20are%20smaller%20scraps%20in%20bits%20and%20pieces%20and%20a%20golden%20light%20that%20is%20gleaming%20from%20inside%20of%20it.%20That%20seemed%20like%20a%20great%20way%20to%20introduce%20the%20creation%20of%20Eve%20in%20her%20most%20powerful%20form%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Econock's%20mantra%20of%20sustainable%20fashion.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-1-1695911661-150x79.jpg%