5-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-3-1695904785-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331150%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParth%20and%20Karishma%20Dalal%20launched%20Reroute%20to%20redefine%20the%20footwear%20industry%20that%20has%20long%20been%20associated%20with%20excessive%20carbon%20emissions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20their%20father%20sadly%20passed%20away%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20Undeterred%2C%20the%20siblings%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20idea%20planted%20by%20their%20father%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20they%20started%20researching%20the%20gaps%20in%20the%20footwear%20industry%20which%20has%20been%20growing%20enormously%20over%20the%20years.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20leather%20or%20synthetic%20rubber%20is%20used%20to%20make%20shoes.%20This%20material%20never%20decomposes%20and%20releases%20toxic%20chemicals%20in%20the%20environment%20which%20contributes%20to%20ozone%20depletion%20and%20global%20warming.%20It%20takes%20twice%20the%20amount%20of%20energy%20and%20water%20to%20manufacture%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parth%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20people%20are%20using%20more%20shoes%20than%20everyday%20%3Cem%3Echappals%20%3C%2Fem%3E(slippers)%20these%20days%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThey%20want%20the%20comfort%20of%20chappals%20in%20shoes%20without%20wearing%20heavy%2C%20leather%20boots.%20So%20we%20decided%20to%20make%20shoes%20that%20are%20lightweight%20and%20can%20be%20worn%20without%20socks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Due%20to%20their%20natural%20makeup%2C%20these%20shoes%20won%E2%80%99t%20make%20your%20feet%20smell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20could%20also%20save%20unnecessary%20piling%20up%20of%20shoes%20in%20landfills%20as%20waste.%20We%20would%20also%20end%20up%20giving%20life%20to%20them%20by%20anot