09-26-at-15.48.00-1695822990-1536x689.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.00-1695822990-150x67.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331080%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERamji%20has%20created%20a%20wall%20musuem%20tracing%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20history%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202018%2C%20and%20an%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20rocket%20model%2C%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20Ramji.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20once%20made%20a%20brass%20model%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EISRO%20rocket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Capacity%20Building%20and%20Public%20Outreach%20(CBPO)%20team%20at%20the%20ISRO%20headquarters%20were%20very%20happy%20with%20the%20model%20and%20called%20me%20for%20a%20meeting.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20build%20more%20rocket%20models%20for%20them.%20This%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20dream%20turning%20into%20a%20reality%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramji.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%2074%2C%20Ramji%20set%20up%20a%20space%20at%20his%20friend%20Moiz%20Vagh%E2%80%99s%20factory%20in%20Mysuru%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20backwards%20since%20then.%20The%20first%20order%20for%20%E2%80%98Craftizan%20Engineering%20models%E2%80%99%20was%20from%20ISRO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20designed%20models%20for%20%E2%80%98ISRO%20on%20wheels%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20were%20six%20buses%20filled%20with%20the%20space%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20satellites%20and%20rockets.%20We%20have%20had%20fantastic%20support%20from%20ISRO%20and%20have%20built%20various%20models%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ramji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E