n%20simply%20work%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20in%20the%20day%20and%20get%20paid%20instantly%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20so%20simple%2C%20that%20anyone%20can%20pick%20it%20up.%20They%20do%20not%20need%20any%20kind%20of%20recording%20space%20or%20anything%20to%20do%20so.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20say%20there%20is%20a%20car%20moving%20in%20the%20background%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20no%20issue%2C%20or%20there%20is%20a%20cow%20mooing%20in%20the%20background%2C%20even%20better!%20The%20companies%20want%20the%20data%20recorded%20in%20a%20natural%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESwarnalata%20Nayak%2C%20who%20records%20her%20voice%20in%20Odiya%20language%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20is%20straightforward%20and%20can%20be%20done%20from%20anywhere.%20After%20finishing%20my%20household%20chores%2C%20I%20assist%20my%20husband%2C%20and%20in%20the%20evenings%20when%20I%20have%20free%20time%2C%20I%20use%20my%20phone%20to%20record%20my%20voice%20for%20Karya.%20They%20pay%20me%20right%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Dignified%20work%E2%80%99%20for%20people%20in%20rural%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20unique%20startup%20took%20nearly%20four%20years%20of%20research%20to%20become%20what%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20came%20to%20Bengaluru%20in%202017%2C%20I%20met%20my%20co-founder%20Vivek%20Seshadri.%20We%20were%20involved%20in%20research%20at%20Microsoft%20Research%20and%20he%20was%20my%20manager%20there.%20It%20is%20where%20we%20both%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20Karya%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-2-1695819984.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20al