e%20years%20in%20business%2C%20the%20company%20has%20made%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F180104%2Fsocial-impact-career-education-impact-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20substantial%20impact.%20%3C%2Fa%3ESo%20far%2C%20they%20have%20worked%20with%2032%2C000%20rural%20Indians%20in%2022%20states%2C%20such%20as%20Maharastra%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20workers%20have%20completed%2035%20million%20hours%20of%20paid%20data.%20We%20have%20collaborations%20with%20companies%20such%20as%20Microsoft%20and%20Google%2C%20foundations%20such%20as%20GATE%20and%20USAIG%2C%20and%20several%20state%20governments%20and%20academia%20like%20Stanford%20and%20IITs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-4-1695820028.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20works%20with%2032%2C000%20people%20from%20rural%20areas%20in%2022%20states%20of%20India.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-4-1695820028.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-4-1695820028-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-4-1695820028-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-4-1695820028-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-4-1695820028-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331054%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20works%20with%2032%2C000%20people%20from%20ru