The%20initiative%20of%20magazines%20in%20schools%20and%20classrooms%20is%20building%20a%20writing%20culture%20among%20students.%20Writing%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20necessary%20practices%20every%20student%20should%20be%20familiar%20with.%20After%20getting%20inspiration%20from%20senior%20students%2C%20junior%20classes%20also%20released%20their%20wall%20magazines%20with%20the%20help%20of%20their%20teachers.%20In%20this%20initiative%2C%20students%20are%20not%20only%20building%20their%20writing%20skills%20but%20learning%20from%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20writing%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kamlesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENPS%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20work%20to%20encourage%20students%20to%20contextualise%20learning%20in%20their%20local%20surroundings.%20Kamlesh%20notes%20that%20the%20school%20identified%20that%20children%20are%20often%20oblivious%20to%20the%20things%20happening%20around%20them%20and%20that%20studying%20only%20within%20classroom%20settings%20without%20context%20or%20reference%20makes%20learning%20more%20abstract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20why%20they%20work%20on%20documenting%20stories%20of%20the%20people%20around%20them%2C%20focussing%20on%20their%20traditional%20art%20and%20craft%2C%20challenges%2C%20social%20issues%2C%20and%20customs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENPS%20collaborates%20with%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Archive%20of%20Rural%20India%20(PARI)%20to%20teach%20students%20reporting%2C%20data%20analysing%2C%20and%20ground%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20project%20is%20helping%20students%20to%20know%20more%20about%20the%20stories%20around%20them%20and%20learn%20from%20the%20ordinary%20people%20of%20day-to-day%20life.%20It%20helps%20senior%20students%20to%20get%20examples%20from%20their%20surroundings%20about%20what%20they%20are%20learning%20in%20the%20classroom.%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20is%20strengthening%20academic%20learning%20and%20helping%20to%20connect%20bookish%20concepts%20with%20the%20stories%20to%20get